hadiths[285]{hadithnumber,text}:
2495,"Ismail-bin-Jafar ne abu-Suhail ( Naafe-bin-Malik-bin-abi-Aamir) se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab Ramazan aata hai, jannat ke darwazey khol diye jatey hain aur dozakh ke darwazey band kar diye jatey hain aur shayatin bediyon mein jakad diye jatey hain."
2496,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se khabar di, unhon-ne ( abu-Suhail Naafe ( ibne-abi Anas se riwayat ki ke unhein unke walid ne bayan kiya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab Ramazan (ki shuruat ( hota hai, rehmat ke darwazey khol diye jatey hain aur dozakh ke darwazey band kar diye jatey hain aur shayatin ko zanjeerein pehna di jati hain."
2497,Saleh ne ibne-Shahab se baqi bachi pichhli sanad se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab Ramazan dakhil ( shuru ( hota hai. ( baqi alfaz ( usi ( Yunus ki hadis) ki tarah hain.
2498,"Yahya-bin-Yahya ne kaha : maine Malik ke samney qirat ki, unhon-ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne Ramazan ka zikr kiya aur farmaya : roza na rakho yahan tak ke chaand dekh lo aur iftaar ( rozon ka ikhtitaam ( na karo yahan tak ke chaand dekh lo aur agar tum par muttala abr-aalood kar (aasman baadlon se bhar) diya jaey to us ( Ramazan ( ki miqdar ( gintii ( poori karo."
2499,"abu-Usama ne kaha : Ubaidullah ne hamein Naafe se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ramazan ka zikr kiya to apne donon hathon se samjhaatey huey farmaya : mahina is tarah aur is tarah aur is tarah hota hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne teesri baar apna angoothaa band kar liya. (yani 29 ki gintii batai ( chaand dekh kar roza rakho aur usey dekh kar rozey khatm karo, agar tumhara aasman baadlon se bhar jaey to iske tees din poorey karo."
2500,"ham se ibne-Numair ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein mere walid ne hadis sunai, kaha : hamein Ubaidullah ne usi ( uper zikr ki gaee (sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, farmaya : agar tum par badal chhaa jayen to iske tees din shumaar karo. jis tarah abu-Usama ki hadis hai."
2501,"Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Ubaidullah se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ramazan ka zikr karke farmaya : mahina untees ka hota hai, ( ishaarey se kaha : ( mahina is tarah , is tarah aur is tarah ( teen dahaaiyaan hota ( hai aur kaha : uski gintii poori karo aur tees ka lafz nahi bola."
2502,"Ayub ne Naafe se, unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mahina untees ka hota hai (aur faisla chaand se hota hai) isliye na chaand dekhey baghair rozey rakho aur na usey dekhey baghair rozey khatm karo agar aasman abr aalud ho to uski gintii ( tees ( poori karo."
2503,"Salma-bin-Alqama ne Naafe se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mahina untees ka bhi hota hai, jab chaand dekh lo to roza rakho aur jab usey dekh lo to rozey khatm karo, agar tum par badal chhaa jayen to uski gintii poori karo."
2504,Saalim-bin-Abdullah ne hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : jab us ( chaand ( ko dekh lo to roza rakho aur jab usey dekh lo to rozey khatm karo aur agar badal chhaa jayen to us ( mahiney ( ki gintii poori kar lo.
2505,"Abdullah-bin-Dinar se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mahina untees raaton ka bhi hota hai. chaand dekhey baghair roza na rakho aur usey dekhey baghair rozey khatm na karo magar ye ke tum par badal chhaa jaaein. agar tum par badal chhaa jayen to us ( mahiney ( ki gintii poori karo."
2506,"Amr-bin-Dinar ne hamein hadis sunai ke unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna, mahina is tarah, is tarah, aur is tarah hota hai aur teesri baar apna angoothaa band kar liya. (ishaarey se untees 29 ki gintii batai.)"
2507,"abu-Salma ne mujhey bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : mahina untees ka bhi hota hai."
2508,"Musa-bin-Talha ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mahina aisa , aisa aur aisa (yani ( das , das aur nau (9) ka hota hai."
2509,"Shoba ne jabla (bin-Sahem) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mahina hamesha aisey, aisey aur aisey hai aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne donon hathon ke sath donon hathon ki ungli se ishara karke farmaya aur teesri martaba mein aap ne apne daain ya baain angoothey ko band farma liya."
2510,"Shoba ne hamein Aqba-bin-hurriyat se hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mahina untees ka hota hai. Shoba ne teen baar donon hathon ko) dikhaa kar) aik doosrey se joda aur teesri baar angoothaa kam kar liya. Aqba ne kaha : mera khayal hai (phir) unhon ( ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : mahina tees ka hota hai aur (eik baar ( apni donon hatheliyan teen baar aik doosrey ke sath jodeiin."
2511,"Muhammad-bin-mussanna, ibne-Bashar , Muhammad Jafar , Shoba , Aswad-bin-Qais, Saeed-ibne-Umar bin-Saeed, Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kartey hain ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ham ummii ummat ke log hain. na ham likhtey hain aur na ham hisab kartey hain mahina is tarah hota hai aur is tarah aur is tarah aur teesri martaba mein angoothey ko band farma liya, aur mahina is tarah aur is tarah aur is tarah hota hai yani mukammal tees (dinon) kaa."
2512,Sufiyan ne Aswad-bin-Qais se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki aur doosrey mahiney ke tees (dinon) ka zikr nahi kiya.
2513,"Sad-bin-ubaida se riwayat hai unhon-ne farmaya ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik aadmi ko kehtey huey suna ke aaj raat aadha mahina ho gaya to Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne us aadmi se farmaya ke tujhey kis tarah malum hua ke aaj raat aadha mahina ho gaya hai? maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna ke mahina is tarah is tarah aur is tarah aur aap ne apni ungliyon se do martaba das ka ishara farmaya aur apni saari ungliyon se ishara farmaya, ''aur aisa'' teesri baar apne angoothey ko khulney se roka ya mod liya."
2514,"Saeed-bin-Musaiyab , Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya jab tum chaand dekh lo to roza rakho aur jab chaand dekho to iftaar ( eid ( karo agar aasman baadlon se bhara ho to tum tees dinon ke rozey rakho ."
2515,Rabe-bin-Muslim ne Muhammad-bin-Ziyad se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya to tum chaand dekh kar roza rakho aur chaand dekh kar iftaar karo aur agar aasman baadlon se bhara ho to tum rozon ki tadaad poori karo.
2516,Shoba ne Muhammad-bin-Ziyad se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum chaand dekh kar roza rakho aur chaand dekh kar iftaar (eid) karo. to agar tum par mahina posheeda rahe to tum tees rozon ki tadaad poori karo.
2517,"Aaraj ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum chaand dekh kar roza rakho aur chaand dekh kar roza iftaar (eid) karo. to agar tum par mahina posheeda rahe to tum tees rozon ki tadaad poori karo."
2518,"Ali-bin-Mubarak ne Yahya-bin-ibne- Kasir se, unhon-ne abi-Salma se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : unhon-ne farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tum Ramzan-ul-mubarek se na aik din aur na hi do din pahley roza rakho. siwaey us aadmi ke jo us din roza rakhta tha to usey chahiye ke wo rakh ley."
2519,"Muawiya-bin-Salam, ibne- Musanna, abu-Aamir, Hisham, ibne- Musanna, ibne-abi-Umar , abdul-wahaab-bin-abdul-Majeed , Ayub , Zuhair-bin-Harab , Husain bin-Muhammad aur Sheban sab ne Hazrat Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se isi sanad ke sath usi hadis ki tarah riwayat bayan ki."
2520,Mamar ne Zohri se riwayat ki hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qism uthai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik mahine tak apni paak beeviyon ke paas nahi jaeinge Zohri kehtey hain ke mujhey Urwa ne khabar di ke Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai unhon-ne farmaya ke jab untees raatein guzar gain main un raaton ka shumaar karti rahi to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere yahaan tashrif laey. unhon (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ( ne kaha : ( baariyon ki) shuruat mujh se farmayi. maine kaha aey Allah ke rasool aap ne qism khaaii thi ke aap hamarey paas aik maah tak na aaeingey aur aap untees din ke baad tashrif ley aaey hain. main gintii rahi hun. aap ne farmaya beshak mahina untees din ka bhi hota hai.
2521,"Leis, abi-Zubair, Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhon-ne farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik mahine tak apni paak beeviyon (Raziallahu anhu) se alehda rahe they, to aap untiswen din mein hamari taraf tashrif laey to ham ne arz kiya ke aaj unteeswaan din hai phir aap ne farmaya ke mahina untees dinon ka bhi hota hai aur aap ne donon hathon ko teen martaba hilaayaa aur aakhiri martaba mein aik ungli ko band farma liya. (itney yani untees din ka hota hai.)"
2522,"ibne-Juraij , abu-Zubair , Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni paak beeviyon se aik mahine tak alehda rahe untees din guzar janey ke baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamari taraf subah ke waqt tashrif laey to kuchh logon ne aap se arz kiya aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! aap untees dinon ke baad tashrif ley aaey? to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mahina untees ka bhi hota hai. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne hathon ko teen martaba milaayaa, do martaba apne hathon ki saari ungliyon ke sath aur teesri martaba mein nau (9) ungliyon ke sath."
2523,"Hajjaj-bin-Muhammad, ibne-Juraij, Yahya bin-Abdullah-bin Muhammad-bin saifii, Ikrima-bin-Abdur-Rehman-bin-Haris, Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) khabar deti hain ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qism uthai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni kuchh paak beeviyon ke paas aik mahine tak nahi jaengey. to jab untees din guzar gaey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) subah ya Sham unki taraf tashrif le gaey. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kiya gaya ke aey Allah ke Nabi ! aap ne to qism uthai thi ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik mahina tak hamari taraf tashrif nahi laaengey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ke mahina untees dinon ka bhi hota hai."
2524,"Rooh , Suhak , ibne-Juraij se is sanad ke sath hi usi hadis ki tarah riwayat kiya gaya hai."
2525,"Muhammad-bin-Bishr , Ismail-bin-abi-Khalid , Muhammad-bin-Saeed , Hazrat Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne aik hath ko doosrey hath par maara aur farmaya ke mahina is tarah aur is tarah hota hai phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne teesri martaba aik ungli kam farma li."
2526,"Zayda , Ismail , Muhammad-bin-Sad apne bap se riwayat kartey huey farmatey hain ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya ke mahina is tarah aur is tarah aur is tarah se hota hai das aur das aur nau (9) martaba."
2527,"Abdullah-bin-Mubarak , Ismail-bin-abi-Khalid se is sanad ke sath ye riwayat bhi is tarah naql ki gaee hai."
2528,"Kureb ko Sayeda umme-al-fazal-binte-Haaris (Raziallahu anhu) ne saiyedna Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf bheja Sham (Syria) mein, unhon-ne kaha ke main gaya Sham ko aur unka kaam nikal diya aur maine chaand dekha Ramazan ka Sham (Syria) mein Juma ki shab ko (yani panj shanba ki Sham ko) phir Madina aaya aakhir maah mein. aur saiyedna Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha mujh se aur zikr kiya chaand ka ke tum ne Kab dekha? maine kaha : Juma ki shab ko . unhon-ne kaha : tum ne khud dekha ? maine kaha : haan aur logon ne bhi dekha aur roza rakha. saiyedna Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) aur logon ne. to saiyedna Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ke ham ne to hafte ki shab ko dekha aur ham poorey tees rozey rakhengey ya chaand dekh lengey to maine kaha : aap kafi nahi jantey dekhnaa saiyedna Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ka aur unka roza rakhna? aap ne farmaya nahi aisa hi hukm kiya hai ham ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne. aur Yahya-bin-Yahya ko shak hai ke) ‏‏‏‏نَكْتَفِى ( kaha ya ( ‏‏‏‏تَكْتَفِى )."
2529,"Husain , Umar-bin-Murra , abul-Bakhtari se riwayat hai unhon-ne farmaya ke ham Umre ke liye nikley to jab ham wadi nakhla mein utrey to ham ne chaand dekha kuchh logon ne kaha ke ye teesri ka chaand hai. aur kisi ne kaha ke ye do raaton ka chaand hai. to hamari mulaqat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se hui to ham ne unse arz kiya ke ham ne chaand dekha hai. koi kehta hai ke teesri taareekh ka chaand hai. koi kehta hai ke dusri ka chaand hai. to Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke tum ne kis raat chaand dekha tha? to ham ne arz kiya ke falan-falan raat ka to aap ne farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya ke Allah Taala ne dekhney ke liye usey badha diya hai. dar haqiqat usi raat ka chaand hai jis raat tum ne usey dekha."
2530,"Shoba , Amr-ibne- Murra , abu-al-Bakhtarii farmatey hain ke ham ne zaate-irq mein Ramazan ka chaand dekha to ham ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf aik aadmi bheja taake wo chaand ke barey mein aap se poochhey to Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya Allah Taala ne chaand dekhney ke liye badha diya hai. to agar aasman baadlon se bhara ho to gintii poori karo."
2531,"Yazeed-bin-Zuree , Khalid , Hazrat Abdur-Rehman-bin-abi-bakra apne bap se riwayat kartey huey farmatey hain ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke eid ke do maah naaqis nahi hotey aik Ramazan ka doosrey Zil-Hijja kaa."
2532,"Moatamir-bin-Sulaiman , Ishaq-bin-suwed , Khalid , Hazrat Abdur-Rehman-bin-abi-bakra apne bap se riwayat kartey huey farmatey hain. ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya do mahiney naaqis nahi hotey. Khalid ki hadis mein hai ke eid ke do mahiney Ramazan aur Zil-Hijja ke hain. Khalid ki hadis mein hai eid ke donon mahiney , Ramazan aur zul-hijja ."
2533,Hazrat Adii-bin-Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne farmaya ke jab aayat :                                                   (حَتَّىٰ يَتَبَيَّنَ لَكُمُ الْخَيْطُ الْأَبْيَضُ مِنَ الْخَيْطِ الْأَسْوَدِ مِنَ الْفَجْرِ‌) nazil hui. to Hazrat Adi (Raziallahu anhu) ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kiya aey Allah ke rasool ! maine apne takiye ke nichey safaid aur siyah rang ke do dhaagey rakh liye hain. jinki wjah se main raat aur din mein imtiyaz kar leta hun to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumhara takiya bahut chaudaa hai ke jis mein raat aur din samaa gaey hain. wo (dhaaga) to raat ki siyaahii aur din ki roshni hai.
2534,"Fuzail-bin-Sulaiman , abu-Hazim , Hazrat Sahal-bin-Sad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain. jab ye aayat                         (وَكُلُوا وَاشْرَ‌بُوا حَتَّىٰ يَتَبَيَّنَ لَكُمُ الْخَيْطُ الْأَبْيَضُ مِنَ الْخَيْطِ الْأَسْوَدِ) nazil hui to kuchh aadmi safaid dhaaga aur siyah dhaaga ley letey aur jab tak unmein waazeh imtiyaz nazar na aata to khaatey rahtey yahan tak Allah Taala ne lafz ( مِنَ الْفَجْرِ‌ ( (fajr se) nazil farmaya aur safaid dhaagey ki wazaahat ho gaee."
2535,"Abu-Ghassan , abu-Hazim , Sahal-bin-Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab ye aayat nazil hui to kuchh aadmi jab unmein se kisi ka roza rakhney ka irada hota to apne donon paon mein siyah aur safaid dhaagey baandh letey aur jab tak donon dhaagon mein waazeh imtiyaz nazar na aata to khaatey aur peetey rahtey yahan tak ke Allah Taala ne lafz (مِنَ الْفَجْرِ) (fajr se) ‌nazil farmaya to tab malum hua ke siyah w safaid dhaagey se raat aur din murad hai."
2536,"Leis , ibne-Shahab , Saalim-bin-Abdullah , Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kartey huey farmatey hain ke unhon-ne farmaya ke Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) raat ke waqt hi azan de detey they lihaza tum khaatey peetey raho yahan tak ke Hazrat ibne-Umme-Maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) ki azan suno ."
2537,"Yunus , ibne-Shahab , Saalim-bin-Abdullah , Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye irshad farmatey huey suna Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) raat ke waqt hi azan de detey hain. lihaza tum khaatey aur peetey raho yahan tak ke tum Hazrat ibne-Umme-Maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) ki azan suno."
2538,"ibne-Numair , Ubaidullah-bin-Naafe , Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke do muazzan they Hazrat Bilal aur Hazrat Abdullaah-ibne-umme-Maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) jo naa-beenaa they. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) to raat ke waqt hi azan de detey hain lihaza tum khaatey aur peetey raho yahan tak ke Hazrat ibne-Umme-Maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) azan dein. rawi ne kaha ke un donon ki azan mein koi farq nahi tha. siwaey iske ke wo azan de kar utartey they aur ye chadhtey they."
2539,"ibne-Numair , Ubaidullah , Qasim , Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi tarah riwayat kiya hai."
2540,"abu-Usama , Abda , Hammad-bin-Mas'ada , sab ne Ubaidullah se (pichhli donon hadison mein mazkoor un ki) sanadon ke sath ibne-Numair ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki hai."
2541,"Ismail-bin-Ibrahim , Sulaiman-Taimi , abi-Usman , Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tum mein se koi Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ki azan ki wjah se na rukey ya aap ne farmaya ke Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ki pukar sehrii khaney se na rukey. kyonke wo azan detey hain ya farmaya ke wo pukaartey hain taake Namaz mein khada honey wala sehrii ke liye lot jaey. aur tum mein se soney wala jaag jaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farma kar hath seedha kiya aur uper ko buland kiya yahan tak ke aap farmatey ke subah is tarah nahi hoti phir ungliyon ko phaila kar farmaya ke subah is tarah hoti hai."
2542,"Khalid ahmar ne, Sulaiman Taimi , se is sanad ke sath Hazrat Sulaiman Taimi se ye riwayat isi tarah naql ki hai siwaey iske ke usmein unhon-ne farmaya ke fajr wo nahi jo is tarah ho aur aap ne ungliyon ko milaya phir unhein zamin ki taraf jhukaya aur farmaya ke fajr wo hai jo is tarah ho aur shahadat ki ungli ko shahadat ki ungli par rakh kar donon hathon ko phailaayaa."
2543,"Abu-Bakar-ibne-Abi-Sheba , Moatamir-bin-Sulaiman , Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim , Jareer, Moatamir-bin-Sulaiman , is sanad ke sath Hazrat Sulaiman Taimi se isi tarah riwayat naql ki gaee hai. usmein hai ke Hazrat Bilal ki azan is wjah se hoti hai ke tum mein se jo so raha ho wo bedaar ho jaey aur jo Namaz padh raha ho wo lot jaey. Ishaq ne kaha : Jarir ne apni hadis mein kaha hai ke subah is tarah nahi hai. matlab ye ke chaudai mein hai lambai mein nahi hai."
2544,"Abdul-Waris , Abdullah-bin-swada-al-qushairii , Hazrat Samra-bin-Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke maine Muhammad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai aap farmatey hain. ke tum mein se koi sehrii ke waqt Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ki azan se dhokaa na khaaey aur na hi us safedi se jab tak ke wo phail na jaey."
2545,"Ismail-bin-uleih, Abdullah-bin-swada, Hazrat Samra-bin-Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tum mein se koi aadmi Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ki azan se dhokaa na khaaey aur na hi safedi se jo ke subah ke waqt sutuonon ki tarah hoti hai yahan tak ke wo zahir ho jaey."
2546,"Hammad, ibne-zaid, Abdullah-bin-swada-al-qushairii, Hazrat Samra-bin-Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tum mein se koi aadmi Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ki azan se apni sehrii se dhokaa na khaaey aur na hi ufuq ki lambi safedi se yahan tak ke wo phail jaey. Hammad ne apne donon hathon (ke ishaarey ( se bayan kiya kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki murad chaudai mein phailney wali (safedi ( se thi."
2547,"Ubaidullah-bin-Muaz , Shoba , suwaada , Hazrat Samra-bin-Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) khutba detey huey bayan kartey hain ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat hai aap ne farmaya tum mein se koi aadmi Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ki azan se dhokaa na khaaey aur na us safedi se yahan tak ke fajr zahir ho jaey."
2548,Abu-Dawud ( Tiyalisi ( ne Shoba se baqi bachi pichhli sanad ke sath riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya........ .iske baad yahi (hadis) bayan ki.
2549,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke sehrii khaya karo kyonke sehrii ke khaney mein barkat hoti hai.
2550,"Leis , Musa-bin-Ali , abi-Qais , Maula Amr-bin-Aas , Hazrat Amr-bin-al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya : hamarey rozey aur ahle-kitab ke rozey ke darmyan sehrii khaney ka farq hai."
2551,Wakee aur ibne- Wahab donon ne Musa-bin-Ali se isi tarah riwayat naql ki hai.
2552,"Hisham , Qatada , Anas , Hazrat Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne farmaya ke ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath sehrii khaaii phir Namaz ke liye khadey huey maine arz kiya ke sehrii khaney aur Namaz ke darmyan kitna waqfa tha aap ne farmaya pachaas aayaton ke barabar ."
2553,"Amr-Nafiz , Yazid-bin-Harun , Hammam , ibne- Musanna , Saalim-bin-Nooh , Umar-bin-Aamir , Qatada se isi sanad ke sath Hazrat Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat naql ki gaee hai."
2554,"Abdul-Azeez-bin-abi-Hazim , Hazrat Sahal-bin-Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya log hamesha bhalai ke sath raheingey jab tak roza jald iftaar kartey raheingey."
2555,"Quteba , Yaqoob , Zuhair-bin-Harab , Abdur-Rehman ibne- Mehdi , Sufiyan , Hazrat Sahal-bin-Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi hadis mubaraka ki tarah riwayat naql ki hai."
2556,"Yahya-bin-Yahya , abu-Kuraib , Muhammad-bin-Alaa , abu-Muawiya , Aamash , Umara-bin-Umair , Hazrat abu-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhon-ne farmaya ke main aur Masruq donon ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya aey Ummul-Momenin ! Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sathiyon mein se do aadmi hain unmein se aik iftaarii mein jaldi karta hai. aur Namaz mein bhi jaldi karta hai. doosra sathi iftaarii mein taakheer karta hai aur Namaz mein bhi taakheer karta hai. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya ! ke unmein se wo kon hain jo iftaarii mein jaldi kartey hain aur Namaz bhi jaldi padhtey hain? Hazrat abu Atiya kehtey hain ke ham ne arz kiya ke wo Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) hain. yani ibne-Masood , Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi isi tarah kiya kartey they abu-Kuraib ki riwayat mein itna zayed hai ke doosrey sathi abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) hain."
2557,"ibne-abi-Zayda , Aamash , Umara , Hazrat abu-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhon-ne farmaya ke main aur Hazrat Masruq (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to aap se Hazrat Masruq (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sathiyon mein se do aisey hain jo bhalai ke barey mein kami nahi kartey. unmein se aik maghrib ki Namaz aur iftaarii mein jaldi karta hai. doosra maghrib ki Namaz aur iftaarii mein taakheer karta hai. to Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya ke maghrib ki Namaz aur iftaarii mein kon jaldi karta hai? Masruq (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya ke Hazrat Abdullah to Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi isi tarah kiya kartey they."
2558,"Yahya-bin-Yahya , abu-Kuraib , ibne-Numair , Yahya , abu-Muawiya , ibne-Numair , abu-Kuraib , Usama , Hisham , Urwa , Aasim , ibne-Umar , Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab raat aa jaey aur din chala jaey aur suraj ghurub ho jaey to roza rakhney waley ko roza iftaar kar lena chahiye ibne-Numair ne ( فقد ( ) haqeeqatan (ka lafz bayan nahi kiya."
2559,"Hushaim , abi-Ishaq-Shebani , Hazrat Abdullah-bin-abi-Ufa se riwayat hai unhon-ne farmaya ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Ramazan ke mahiney mein aik safar mein they jab suraj ghurub ho gaya to aap ne farmaya aey falan ! utar aur hamarey liye sattu mila. us ne arz kiya aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! abhi to din hai Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya utar aur hamarey liye sattu mila to wo utra aur us ne sattu mila kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kiya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sattu piyaa phir aap ne apne hath Mubarak se farmaya jab suraj us taraf se ghurub ho jaey aur us taraf se raat aa jaey to roza rakhney waley ko iftaar kar lena chahiye. (uska roza khatm ho chuka)"
2560,"Ali-bin-Mus'hir , Ibad-bin-awaam , Shebani , Hazrat ibne-abi-Ufa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhon-ne farmaya ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik safar mein they jab suraj ghurub ho gaya to aap ne aik aadmi se farmaya utar aur hamarey liye sattu mila. us ne arz kiya aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) agar aap Sham honey dein? to aap ne farmaya utar aur hamarey liye sattu mila. us ne arz kiya abhi to din hai wo utra aur us ne sattu milaya aap ne sattu piyaa phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab tum dekho ke raat us taraf aa gaee hai aur aap ne mashriq ki taraf apne hath se ishara farmaya to roze-daar ko roza iftaar kar lena chahiye."
2561,"abu-Kaamil , abdul-Wahid , Sulaiman Shebani , Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Ufa (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik safar mein they aur aap roze ki haalat mein they, to jab suraj ghurub ho gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aey falan ! utar aur hamarey liye sattu mila aagey hadis isi tarah hai."
2562,"ibne-abi-Umar , Sufiyan , Ishaq , Jareer, Shebani , ibne-abi-Ufa , Ubaidullah-bin-Muaz , ibne- Musanna , Muhammad-bin-Jafar , Shoba is sanad ke sath Hazrat ibne- oofaa (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se is tarah riwayat naql ki hai lekin usmein kuchh alfaz ki kami hai."
2563,"Yahya-bin-Yahya , Naafe , Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne saume-wisaal (raat-din lagaataar roza rakhne) se mana farmaya hai sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ne arz kiya ke aap to wisaal kartey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main tumhari tarah nahi hun kyonke mujhey to khilaaya aur pilaya jata hai."
2564,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , Abdullah-bin-Numair , Ubaidullah , Naafe , Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ramazan mein wisaal farmaya (yani baghair iftaarii ke musalsal rozey rakhey) lihaza sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ne bhi wisaal shuru kar diya to aap ne unko mana farmaya, aap se arz kiya gaya ke aap bhi to wo wisaal kartey hain. aap ne farmaya ke main tumhari tarah nahi hun kyonke mujhey khilaaya aur pilaya jata hai."
2565,"Abdul-Waris-bin-Abdus-Samad , Ayub , Naafe , ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi hadis ki tarah naql farmaya hai lekin usmein Ramazan ka lafz nahi."
2566,"Hurmala-bin-Yahya , ibne- Wahab , Yunus , ibne-Shahab , abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman , Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhon-ne farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wisaal se mana farmaya musalmanon mein se aik aadmi ne arz kiya ke aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! aap bhi to musalsal rozey rakhtey hain. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tum mein se meri tarah kon hai? main to us haalat mein raat guzaarta hon ke mera rab mujhey khilata aur pilaataa hai. jab iske bawajud sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) saume-wisaal (raat-din lagaataar roza rakhne) se na rukey to aap ne unke sath aik iftaarii ke baghair roza rakha aur phir iftaar ke baghair roza rakha phir unhon-ne chaand dekh liya aap ne farmaya ke agar chaand taakheer karta to main aur zyada wisaal karta maano ke aap ne unke na rukney par na-pasandidgi ka izhar farmaya."
2567,"Zuhair-bin-Harab , Ishaq , Zuhair , Jareer, Umara , abi zar'a , Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum wisaal ke rozey rakhney se bacho. sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ne arz kiya aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! aap bhi to wisaal ke rozey rakhtey hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum us mamley mein meri tarah nahi ho kyonke main us haalat mein raat guzaarta hon ke mera rab mujhey khilata aur pilaataa hai. to tum wo kaam karo jiski tum taqat rakhtey ho."
2568,"Quteba , Mughira , abi-zinaad , Aaraj , Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi tarah riwayat kiya hai siwaey iske ke usmein hai Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya jis kaam ki tum taqat rakho wo kaam karo."
2569,"ibne-Numair , Aamash , abi-Saleh , Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi tarah riwayat kiya hai jis mein hai ke aap ne wisaal se mana farmaya, ( aagey ( abu-Zura se Umara ki hadis ki tarah hai."
2570,"Zuhair-bin-Harab , abu-Nazar Hashim-bin-Qasim , Sulaiman , Sabit , Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Ramazan mein Namaz padh rahe they, to main aa kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke pahlu ki taraf khada ho gaya, aik aur aadmi aaya wo bhi khada ho gaya, yahan tak ke hamari aik jamat bin gaee. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mehsus farmaya ke main aap ke peechhey hon to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz mein kami (kamii) shuru farma di. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghar mein dakhil huey. aap ne aik aisi Namaz padhi jaisi Namaz aap hamarey sath nahi padhtey they jab subah hui to ham ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kiya ke kya raat aapko hamara ilm ho gaya tha? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya haan usi wjah se wo kaam kiya jo maine kiya. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wisaal ke rozey rakhney shuru farma diye wo mahine ke aakhir mein they. aap ke sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) mein se bhi kuchh logon ne wisaal ke rozey rakhney shuru kar diye to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ke ye log saume-wisaal (raat-din lagaataar roza rakhne) kyon rakh rahe hain? tum log meri tarah nahi ho Allah ki qism ! agar ye mahina lamba hota to main is qadr wisaal ke rozey rakhta ke zid karne waley apni zid chhod detey.''"
2571,"Aasim-bin-nazar Taimi , Khalid , ibne- Haris , Humaid , Sabit , Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ramazan ke mahine ke aakhir mein wisaal ke rozey rakhey to musalmanon mein se kuchh logon ne wisaal ke rozey rakhney shuru kar diye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak ye baat pahunchi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya agar hamarey liye ye mahina lamba ho jaey to main is qadr wisaal ke rozey rakhta ke zid karne waley apni zid chhod detey. kyonke tum meri tarah nahi ho Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ''main tumhari tarah nahi hun main to us haalat mein raat guzaarta hun, ke mera rab mujhey khilata aur pilaataa hai.''"
2572,"Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim , Usman-bin-abi-Sheba , Abda-bin-Sulaiman , Hisham-bin-Urwa , Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unko shafqat ke taur par wisaal ke rozon se mana farmaya. sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ne arz kiya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) to wisaal ke rozey rakhtey hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main tumhari tarah nahi hun. kyonke mera rab mujhey khilata aur pilaataa hai.''"
2573,"Ali-bin hijr , Sufiyan , Hisham-bin-Urwa , Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni paak beeviyon mein se kisi ka bosa ley liya kartey they. jabke aap rozey se hotey they. Hazrat Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) muskuraa padiin."
2574,"Ali-bin-hijr , ibne-abi-Umar , Sufiyan farmatey hain ke maine Abdur-Rehman-bin-Qasim se puchha ke kya tum ne apne bap ko Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat bayan kartey huey suna ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) roze ki haalat mein unka bosa ley liya kartey they? Hazrat Abdur-Rehman thodi der khamosh rahe phir farmaya haan."
2575,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , Ali-bin-Mus'hir , Ubaidullah-bin-Umar , Qasim , Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) roze ki haalat mein mera bosa ley liya kartey they. aur tum mein se kon hai jo apne jazbaat ko qaabu mein kar sakey jis tarah ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko apne jazbaat par control (qaabu) tha."
2576,"Yahya-bin-Yahya , abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , abu-Kuraib , Yahya , abu-Muawiya , Aamash , Ibrahim , Aswad , Alqama , Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) roze ki haalat main apni paak beeviyon ka bosa ley liya kartey they aur roze ki haalat mein unse baghalgeer ho jaya kartey they. lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) to tum mein se sabse zyada apne jazbaat ko control (qaabu) mein rakhney waley they."
2577,"Ali-bin-hijr , Zuhair-bin-Harab , Sufiyan , Mansoor , Ibrahim , Alqama , saiyeda  Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) roze ki haalat main apni kisi bevi ka bosa ley liya kartey they aur aapko to tum mein se sabse zyada apne jazbaat par control (qaabu) tha."
2578,"Muhammad-bin-Musanna , ibne-Bashar , Muhammad-bin-Jafar , Shoba , Mansoor , Ibrahim , Alqama , Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni kisi paak bevi se roze ki haalat mein baghalgeer ho jaya kartey they."
2579,"Muhammad-bin-Musanna , abu-Aasim , Ibne-Aun , Ibrahim , Aswad , farmatey hain ke main aur Masruq Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein aaey to ham ne aap se arz kiya ke kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) roze ki haalat main apni kisi bevi se baghl-geer ho jaya kartey they? Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya haan lekin aap ko tum mein sabse zyada apne jazbaat par control rakhney waley they. ya farmaya ke tum mein se kon hai jo aap ki tarah apne jazbaat qaabu mein rakh sakey? abu-Aasim rawi ko shak hai. ( mafhoom aik hi hai)"
2580,"Yaqoob , Ismail , Ibne-Aun , Ibrahim , Aswad , Masruq is sanad ke sath Ibrahim se Hazrat Aswad aur Hazrat Masruq ke barey mein riwayat hai ke wo donon Ummul-Momenin ke paas aaey aur aap se puchha phir aa kar isi tarah hadis zikr farmai."
2581,"Abu-Bakar-ibne-Abi-Sheba , Hasan-bin- Musa , Sheban , Yahya-ibne-abi Kasir , abi Salma , Umar-bin-Abdul-Azeez , Urwa-bin-Zubair , Ummul-Momenin Sayeda Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) khabar deti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rozey ki haalat mein mera bosa ley liya kartey they."
2582,"Yahya ibne-Bishr hareerii , Muawiya , Hazrat Yahya-bin-Kasir se is sanad ke sath isi tarah riwayat naql ki gaee hai."
2583,"Yahya-ibne- Yahya , Qutaiba-bin-Saeed , abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , abu-Ahwas , Ziyad-bin-ilaqa , Amr-bin-Memoon , saiyeda Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rozon ke mahiney main apni kisi bevi ka bosa ley liya kartey they."
2584,"Muhammad-bin-Hatim , bahaz-bin-Asad , Abu-Bakar-nehshali, Ziyad-bin-ilaqa , Amr-bin-Memoon , Sayeda Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) roze ki haalat main apni paak bevi (Raziallahu anhu) ka bosa ley liya kartey they."
2585,"Muhammad-bin-Bashar , Abdur-Rehman , Sufiyan , abi-zanaad , Ali-bin-Husain , Sayeda Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni paak bevi ka roze ki haalat mein bosa ley liya kartey they."
2586,"Yahya-bin-Yahya , abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , abu-Kuraib , Yahya , abu-Muawia , Aamash , Muslim , Shutair-bin-shakl , Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) roze ki haalat main apni paak bevi ka bosa ley liya kartey they."
2587,"abu-Rabe-Zahrani , abu-Awana , abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim , Jareer, Mansoor , Muslim, Shutair-bin- shakl , Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) is sanad ke sath Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi tarah hadis naql farmai hai."
2588,"Haroon-bin-Saeed, ibne- Wahab , Amr , ibne- Haris , abde-rabbi-bin-Saeed, Abdullah-bin-Kab-himyerii , Hazrat Umar-bin-abi-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha ke roze-daar bosa ley sakta hai? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hazrat Umar-bin Salma (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke ye Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se poochho to Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne unhein khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) isi tarah kartey hain. Hazrat Umar-bin-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! Allah Taala ne to aap ke agley pichhley gunah sarey maaf farma diye hain. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hazrat Umar-bin-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya suno ! Allah ki qism ! main tum mein sabse zyada taqwa wala aur Allah se darney wala hun."
2589,"Muhammad-bin-Hatim , Yahya-bin-Saeed , ibne-Juraij , Muhammad-bin-Raafe , Abdur-Razzaq-bin-Hammam , ibne-Juraij , Abdul-Malik -bin-abi-Bakr-bin-Abdur-Rehman , Abu-Bakar se riwayat hai unhon-ne farmaya ke maine Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna ke wo apni riwayat bayan kartey hain jis aadmi ne junbi (hambistari ke baad ki napaki ki haalat me) haalat mein subah ki to wo roza na rakhey , rawi Abu-Bakar farmatey hain ke maine iska zikr apne bap Abdur-Rehman-bin-Haris se kiya to unhon-ne iska inkar kar diya, to Hazrat Abdur-Rehman chaley aur main bhi unke sath chala yahan tak ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) aur Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir huey. Hazrat Abdur-Rehman ne un donon se us barey mein puchha to unhon-ne farmaya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ehtilam ke baghair junbi (hambistari k baad ki napaki ki haalat me) honey ki haalat mein subah kartey phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) roza rakhtey. rawi kehtey hain ke phir ham chaley yahan tak ke Marwan ke paas aagey Hazrat Abdur-Rehman ne Marwan se us barey mein zikr kiya to Marwan ne kaha ke main tum par lazim karta hun ke tum zaroor Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf jao aur uski tardeed karo. jo wo kehtey hain to ham Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey aur Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) bhi wahan maujood they Hazrat Abdur-Rehman ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se ye Sara kuchh zikr kiya Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya kya un donon ne tujh se yahi farmaya hai? Hazrat Abdur-Rehman ne kaha ke haan! Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke wo donon us masle ko zyada janti hain. phir Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne us qaul ki jo ke aap ne Fazal-bin-Abbaas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna tha uski tardeed kar di aur Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke maine ye Fazal-bin-Abbaas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna tha aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se nahi suna rawi kehtey hain ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne qaul ko waapis le liya jo wo kaha kartey they. rawi kehtey hain ke maine Abdul-Malik se kaha ke kya un donon ne ye hadis Ramazan ke barey mein bayan ki thi? unhon-ne kaha ke aap baghair ehtilam ke junbi (hambistari k baad ki napaki ki haalat me) haalat mein subah uthtey phir aap roza rakhtey."
2590,"Hurmala-bin-Yahya , ibne- Wahab , Yunus , ibne-Shahab , Urwa-bin-Zubair , abi-Bakr-bin-Abdur-Rehman , Sayeda Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Ramazan mein junbi (hambistari k baad ki napaki ki haalat me) haalat mein baghair ehtilam ke subah uthtey phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghusl farmatey aur roza rakhtey."
2591,"Haron-bin-Saeed, ibne- Wahab , Amr , ibne- Haris , abde-rabbi , Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Kab-himyerii (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Marwan ne unko Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ki taraf aik aadmi ke barey mein poochhney ke liye bheja ke wo junbi (hambistari ke baad ki napaki ki haalat me) haalat mein subah uthtaa hai kya wo roza rakh sakta hai? to Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hambistari ki wjah se junbi (hambistari k baad ki napaki ki haalat me) haalat mein baghair ehtilam ke subah uthtey phir aap iftaar na kartey aur na hi uski qaza kartey."
2592,"Yahya-bin-Yahya , Malik , abde-rabbi , bin-Saeed, abi-Bakr-bin-Abdur-Rehman-bin-Haris-bin-Hisham , Sayeda Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) aur Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak beeviyan farmati hain. ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Ramazan mein hambistari ki wjah se na ke ehtilam ki wjah se junbi (hambistari k baad ki napaki ki haalat me) haalat mein subah kartey phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) roza rakhtey they."
2593,"Yahya-bin-Yahya , Ayub , Quteba , ibne- hijr , ibne- Ayub , Ismail-bin-Jafar , Abdullah-bin-Abdur-Rehman , ibne- Mamar bin-Hazam Ansari , abu-tawaala , Yunus , Sayeda Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke aik aadmi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein koi masla poochhney ke liye aaya aur wo darwaze ke peechhey se sun rahi thin. us aadmi ne kaha aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) junbi (hambistari k baad ki napaki ki haalat me) haalat mein hota hun ke Namaz ka waqt ho jata hai to kya main us waqt roza rakh sakta hoon? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya main bhi to Namaz ke waqt junbi (hambistari k baad ki napaki ki haalat me) haalat mein uthtaa hon to main bhi to roza rakhta hun. to us aadmi ne kaha aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! aap hamari tarah to nahi hain aap ke to agley-pichhley gunah Allah ne maaf farma diye hain. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah ki qism ! mujhey ummeed hai ke main tum mein sabse zyada darney wala hun aur main tum mein sabse zyada janta hun un chizon ko jin se bachna chahiye."
2594,"Ahmed-bin-Usman-naufalii , abu-Aasim , ibne-Juraij , Muhammad-bin-Yousuf , Hazrat Sulaiman-bin-Yasar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se aik aadmi ke barey mein puchha ke wo junbi (hambistari k baad ki napaki ki haalat me) haalat mein subah karta hai to kya wo aadmi roza rakh sakta hai? Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) junbi (hambistari k baad ki napaki ki haalat me) haalat mein baghair ehtilam ke subah kartey phir aap roza rakhtey."
2595,"Yahya-bin-Yahya , abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , Zuhair-bin-Harab , ibne-Numair , ibne-Uena , Sufiyan-bin-Uena, Humaid-bin-Abdur-Rehman , Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke aik aadmi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur us ne arz kiya aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! main halaak ho gaya aap ne farmaya to kaisey halaak ho gaya? us ne arz kiya ke maine Ramazan main apni biwi se ham-bistarii kar li hai aap ne farmaya kya to aik ghulam aazad kar sakta hai? us ne arz kiya nahi, aap ne farmaya kya to musalsal do mahiney ke rozey rakh sakta hai? us ne arz kiya nahi, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya to saath (60) miskinon ko khana khila sakta hai? us ne arz kiya ke nahi, rawi kehtey hain ke phir wo aadmi baith gaya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aik tokraa laya gaya jis mein khajoorein thin. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya unko mohtajon mein sadqa kar do us ne arz kiya, kya ham se bhi zyada mohtaaj hai? Madina ke donon aas-paas ke darmyan waley gharon mein koi aisa ghar nahi jo ham se zyada mohtaaj ho. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hans padey. yahan tak ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki daadhein Mubarak zahir ho gain. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us aadmi se farmaya ja aur usey apne ghar walon ko khila ."
2596,"Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim , Jareer, Mansoor , Muhammad-bin-Muslim Zohri (Raziallahu anhu) se is sanad ke sath is tarah riwayat naql ki gaee hai aur rawi ne kaha ke usmein us tokrey ka zikr nahi hai. jis mein khajoorein thin. yani zanbeel aur wo ye bhi zikr nahi kartey ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hansey yahan tak ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki daadhein zahir ho gain ."
2597,"Yahya-bin-Yahya , Muhammad-bin-Rumeh , Leis , Quteba , ibne-Shahab , Humaid-bin-Abdur-Rehman , bin-Auf , Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke aik aadmi ne Ramazan main apni biwi se ham-bistari kar li aur phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us masle ke barey mein puchha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya to aik ghulam aazad kar sakta hai? us ne arz kiya nahi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya to do mahiney ke rozey rakh sakta hai? us ne arz kiya nahi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya to phir to sath miskinon ko khana khila de."
2598,"Muhammad-bin Raafe , Ishaq-bin-Esa , Malik , Zohri se isi sanad ke sath riwayat hai ke aik aadmi ne Ramazan mein roza iftaar kar liya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey hukm farmaya ke aik ghulam aazad karke kaffara ada karey phir ibne-Uena ki hadis ki tarah hadis zikr farmai."
2599,"Muhammad-bin Raafe , Abdur-Razzaq , ibne-Juraij , ibne-Shahab , Humaid-bin-Abdur-Rehman , Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik aadmi ko hukm farmaya jis aadmi ne Ramazan mein roza tod liya tha usey chahiye ke wo aik ghulam aazad karey ya do mahiney ke rozey rakhey ya saath (60) miskinon ko khana khilaey."
2600,Mamar ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath ibne-Uena ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki.
2601,"Muhammad-bin-Rumeh , ibne- muhajir , Leis , Yahya-bin-Saeed , Abdur-Rehman-bin-Qasim , Muhammad-bin-Jafar , ibne-Zubair , Ibad-bin-Abdullah-bin Zuber , Sayeda Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke aik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur us ne arz kiya main to jal gaya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kyon? usne kaha ke maine Ramazan ke dinon main apni biwi se ham-bistari kar li hai, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya sadqa kar, sadqa kar, us aadmi ne arz kiya ke mere paas to kuchh bhi nahi hai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey hukm farmaya ke wo baith jaey to aap ki khidmat mein do tokrey aaey jis mein khana tha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us aadmi ko hukm farmaya ke usko sadqa karo."
2602,"Muhammad-bin-Musanna , abdul-wahaab Saqafi , Yahya-bin-Saeed , Abdur-Rehman-bin-Qasim , Muhammad-bin-Jafar-bin-Zubair , Abdullah-bin-Zubair , Sayeda Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke aik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur phir hadis zikr ki aur is mein sadqe ka zikr nahi hai aur na hi din ka zikr hai."
2603,"abu-Taahir , ibne- Wahab , Amr-bin-Haris , Abdur-Rehman-bin-Qasim , Muhammad-bin-Jafar-bin-Zubair , Ibad-bin-Abdullah-bin-Zubair , Sayeda Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi farmati hain. aik aadmi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein Ramazan mein masjid mein aaya aur us ne arz kiya aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! main to jal gaya, main to jal gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se puchha ke kya hua? to usne arz kiya ke maine apni biwi se ham-bistari kar li hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya sadqa kar, to usne arz kiya Allah ki qism ! aey Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere paas to kuchh bhi nahi, aur main is par qudrat bhi nahi rakhta . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : baith ja , to wo baith gaya. usi doran aik aadmi apna gadhaa haanktey huey laya jis par khana rakha hua tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo jalney wala aadmi kahan hai? wo aadmi khada hua to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : isko sadqa kar to us aadmi ne arz kiya aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! kya hamarey ilawa bhi (koii sadqe ka mustahiq hai) Allah ki qism ham bhookey hain, hamarey paas kuchh bhi nahi hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tum hi isey kha lo."
2604,"Yahya-bin-Yahya , Muhammad-bin-Rumeh , Leis , Quteba , bin-Saeed, ibne-Shahab , Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullaah-bin-Utba , Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) fateh Makka waley saal Ramazan mein nikley to aap ne roza rakha jab aap kudaid ke maqam par pahunchey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne roza iftaar kar liya. rawi ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke har naey se naey hukm ki pairwi kiya kartey they."
2605,"Yahya-bin-Yahya abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , umr , Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim , Sufiyan , Zohri , se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah hadis naql ki gaee hai Sufiyan ne kaha ke mujhey nahi malum ke ye kis ka qaul hai aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aakhiri qaul ko liya jata tha."
2606,"Muhammad-bin Raafe , Abdur-Razzaq , Mamar , Zohri se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah riwayat naql ki gaee hai aur Zohri ne kaha ke roza iftaar karna aakhiri amal tha aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aakhiri amal ko hi apnaayaa jata hai Zohri ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Ramazan ki 13 taareekh ko Makka Mukarrama pahunchey."
2607,"Hurmala-bin-Yahya , ibne- Wahab , Yunus , ibne-Shahab Leis is sanad ke sath ibne-Shahab se Leis ki hadis ki tarah riwayat naql ki gaee hai ibne-Shahab ne farmaya ke wo log Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aakhiri amal ki pairwi kartey they aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke puraaney amal ko naasikh qarar detey they."
2608,"Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim , Jareer, Mansoor , Mujahid , Taaus , hazrat-Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Ramazan mein aik safar mein they, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne roza rakha , jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Asfan ke maqam par pahunchey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik bartan mangwaya jis mein koi peeney ki cheez thi, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey din ke waqt mein piyaa taake log usey dekh lein. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne roza nahi rakha yahan tak ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka mein dakhil ho gaey. Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne safar ke doran roza rakha bhi aur nahi bhi rakha to jo chahey safar mein roza rakh ley aur jo chahey roza na rakhey."
2609,"abu-Kuraib , Wakee , Sufiyan , Abdul-Karim , Taaus , Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhon-ne farmaya ke ham bura-bhala nahi kehtey they ke jo roza rakhey aur na hi bura bhala kehtey hain jo aadmi safar mein roza na rakhey. tahqeeq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne safar mein roza rakha bhi aur roza iftaar bhi kiya hai."
2610,"Muhammad-bin-Musanna , abdul-wahaab , ibne- Abdul-Majeed , Jafar , Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) fateh Makka waley saal Ramazan main Makka ki taraf nikley to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne roza rakha jab aap kara'al-ghameem ( کراع الغمیم ( pahunchey to logon ne bhi roza rakha phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pani ka aik piyala mangwaya phir usey buland kiya yahan tak ke logon ne usey dekh liya. phir aap ne wo pi liya iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kiya gaya ke kuchh logon ne roza rakha hua hai. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye log naafarmaan hain, ye log naafarmaan hain."
2611,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed , Abdul-Azeez , Hazrat Jafar se isi sanad ke sath ye riwayat naql ki gaee hai aur is mein ye zayed hai ke aap se arz kiya gaya ke logon par roza dushwar ho raha hai aur wo us barey mein intizar kar rahe hain ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kya kartey hain? to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Asr ke baad pani ka aik piyala mangwaya ."
2612,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , Muhammad-bin-Musanna , ibne-Bashar , Muhammad-bin-Jafar ( ghandar ( Shoba , Muhammad-bin-Abdur-Rehman , ibne- Sad , Muhammad-bin-Amr-bin-Hasan , Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhon-ne farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik safar mein they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik aadmi ko dekha ke log uske ird-gird jama hain aur is par saaya kiya gaya hai. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ke us aadmi ko kya hua hai? logon ne arz kiya ye aik aadmi hai jisne roza rakha hua hai tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ye neki nahi ke tum safar mein roza  rakho."
2613,"Ubaidullah-bin-Muaz , Shoba , Muhammad-bin-Abdur-Rehman , Muhammad-bin-Amr-bin-Hasan , Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik aadmi ko dekha baqi hadis isi tarah hai."
2614,"Ahmed-bin-Usman-naufalii , Abu-Dawud , Shoba , Yahya ibne-abi-kaseer is tarah aik aur sanad ke sath bhi ye riwayat naql ki gaee hai jis mein hai ke Allah Taala ne tumhen jo rukhsat (choot) ata farmai hai is par amal karna tumharey liye zaroori hai rawi ne kaha ke jab maine unse sawal kya to unko yad nahi tha."
2615,"Haddab-bin-Khalid , Hammam-bin-Yahya , Qatada , abu-Nazara , Hazrat Abu-Saeed-Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhon-ne farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath sola Ramazan ko aik jang mein gaey to ham mein se kuchh log rozey se they aur kuchh baghair rozey ke chunanche na to roza rakhney walon ne na rakhney walon ki mazammat ki aur na hi na rakhney walon ne rakhney walon par koi nakeer ki."
2616,"Muhammad-bin-abi-Bakr-muqaddamii , Yahya-bin-Saeed Taimi , Muhammad-bin-Musanna , ibne- Mehdi , Shoba , abu-Aamir , Hisham , Saalim-bin-Nooh , umr ( ibne- Aamir ( abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba is sanad ke sath Hazrat Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se Hammam ki hadis ki tarah riwayat kiya gaya hai siwaey iske ke Taimi aur Umar-bin-Aamir aur Hisham ki riwayat mein atthaara taareekh aur Saeed ki hadis mein baara taareekh aur Shoba ki hadis mein satrah ya unnees taareekh zikr ki gaee hai."
2617,"Nasar-bin-Ali-jahazmii , Bishr ( ibne- Mufazzal ( abi Muslima , abi nazara , Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke Ramazan mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik safar mein they, to koi bhi roza rakhney waley ke roze par tanqeed nahi karta tha aur na hi roze ke iftaar karne waley par koi tanqeed karta tha."
2618,"Amr-Naqid , Ismail-bin-Ibrahim , Jurairi , abi nazara , Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne farmaya ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Ramazan mein aik jang mein they, to ham mein se koi roze-daar hota aur koi iftaar karne wala hota, to na to roze-daar iftaar karne waley par tanqeed karta. wo ye samajhtey they ke agar koi taqat rakhta hai to roza rakh ley to ye uske liye achchha hai aur wo ye bhi samajhtey agar koi zauf (kamzoor) paata hai, to wo iftaar kar ley to ye uske liye achchha hai."
2619,"Saeed-bin-Umar , Sahal-bin-Usman , suwed-bin-Saeed, Husain-bin-hurriyat , Saeed, Marwan-bin-Muawiya , Aasim , abu-nazara , Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri , aur Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai farmaya ke ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath safar kiya to roza rakhney wala roza rakhta aur iftaar karne wala roza iftaar kar leta tha aur unmein se koi kisi ko malaamat nahi karta tha."
2620,"Yahya-bin-Yahya , abu-khaisma , Humaid se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se safar mein Ramazan ke rozey ke barey mein puchha gaya to unhon-ne farmaya ke ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath safar kiya hai to koi roza rakhney wala, roza chhodney waley ko malaamat nahi karta tha aur na hi roza chhodney wala, roze rakhney waley ko malaamat karta tha."
2621,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , abu-Khalid Ahmar , Humaid se riwayat hai, farmaya ke main nikla aur maine roza rakh liya to logon ne mujh se kaha ke tum dobara roza rakho maine kaha Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey khabar di hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) safar kartey they, to koi bhi roza rakhney wala roza chhodney waley ki malaamat nahi karta tha aur na hi roza chhodney wala roza rakhney waley ki malaamat karta tha. phir maine ibne-abi-Mulaika se mulaqat ki to unhon-ne bhi Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke hawale se isi tarah ki khabar di."
2622,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , abu-Muawiya , Aasim , muwarriq , Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik safar mein they, to ham mein kuchh roze-daar they aur kuchh roza chhodey huey they. rawi ne kaha ke ham aik jagah sakht garmi ke mausam mein utrey aur ham mein sabse zyada saaya hasil karne wala wo aadmi tha ke jiske paas chadar thi. ham mein se kuchh apne hathon se dhoop se bach rahe they. rawi ne kaha ke roza rakhney waley to gir gaey aur roza chhodney waley qaaim rahe unhon-ne khemey lagaey aur oonton ko pani pilaya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aaj ke din roza chhodney waley ajr hasil kar gaey."
2623,"abu-Kuraib , Hafs , Aasim , muwarriq , Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik safar mein they kuchh ne roza rakha aur kuchh ne roza chhod diya roza na rakhney waley to khidmat ke kaam par lag gaey aur roza rakhney waley khidmat ke kaam mein kamzor pad gaey rawi ne kaha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke barey mein farmaya ke roza iftaar karne waley ajr pa gaey."
2624,"Muhammad-bin-Hatim , Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi , Muawiya-bin-Saleh , Hazrat Rabee se riwayat hai wo kehtey hain ke mujh se Qaza ne bayan kiaya unhon-ne kaha ke main Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya us haal mein ke unke paas logon ka jamghataa laga hua tha to log unse alehda ho gaey to maine unse arz kiya ke main aap se wo nahi poochhoon-gaa jiske barey mein ye poochh rahe hain. (rawi kehtey hain) ke maine safar ke roze ke barey mein puchha to unhon-ne farmaya ke ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Makka Mukarrama tak safar kiya hai, aur ham roze ki haalat mein they unhon-ne farmaya : ke ham aik jagah utrey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum dushman ke qareeb ho gaey ho aur ab iftaar karna (roza na rakhna) tumharey liye quwwat w taqat ka baais hoga, to ye roze ki rukhsat (choot) thi. phir ham mein se kuchh ne roza rakha aur kuchh ne roza na rakha. phir jab ham dusri manzil tak pahunchey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ke tum subah ke waqt apne dushman se saamnaa karogey, roza na rakhney se tumharey andar taqat zyada hogi isliye roza na rakho. ''Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ye hukm zaroori tha isliye ham ne roza nahi rakha.'' phir ham ne dekha ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath safar mein roza rakhtey rahe."
2625,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed , Leis , Hisham-bin-Urwa , Sayeda Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Hazrat Hamza-bin-Umar Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se safar mein rozey rakhney ke barey mein puchha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya ke agar to chahey to roza rakh ley aur agar to chahey to roza iftaar kar ley."
2626,"abu-Rabeea' , Hammad , ibne-zaid , Hisham , Sayeda Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Hamza-bin-Amr Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kiya aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! main aik aisa aadmi hon ke musalsal rozey rakhta hun to kya main safar mein bhi roza rakhoon ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar to chahey to roza rakh ley aur agar chahey to iftaar kar ley."
2627,"Yahya-bin-Yahya , abu-Muawiya , Hazrat Hisham se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah hadis naql ki gaee hai."
2628,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba-abu-Kuraib , ibne-Numair , Abu-Bakar , abdur-Raheem-bin-Sulaiman , Hazrat Hisham se isi sanad ke sath riwayat hai ke Hazrat Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main aik rozey daar aadmi hon to kya main safar mein bhi roza rakhoon?"
2629,"abu-Taahir , Haroon-bin-Saeed, Haroon , abu-Taahir , ibne- Wahab , Amr-bin-Haris , abi-Aswad , Urwa-bin-Zubair , abi-muraawih, Hazrat Hamza-bin-Umar Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhon-ne arz kiya aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! main safar mein rozey rakhney ki taqat rakhta hun to kya mujh par koi gunah to nahi ? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ke ye Allah ki taraf se aik rukhsat (choot) hai to jisne us rukhsat par amal kiya to usne achchha kiya aur jisne roza rakhna pasand kiya to is par koi gunah nahi. Haroon ne apni hadis mein ''rukhsat'' (رخصۃ) ka lafz kaha hai aur  ''Allah ki taraf se'' ka zikr nahi kiya."
2630,"Dawood-bin-rasheed , Waleed-bin-Muslim , Saeed-bin-Abdul-Azeez , Ismail , Ubaidullah , Umme- Darda (Raziallahu anhu) , Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Ramazan ke mahiney mein garmi ke mausam mein aik safar mein nikley yahan tak ke garmi ki wjah se ham mein se kuchh log apne hathon ko apne sar par rakh letey they aur ham mein se koi bhi roze-daar nahi tha siwaey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Hazrat Abdullaah-bin-Rawaaha (Raziallahu anhu) ke."
2631,"Abdullaah-bin-Maslima , Hisham-bin-Saeed, Usman-ibne- Hayyan Dimashqi , Hazrat Umme- Darda (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Hazrat abu Darda (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath sakht garmiyon ke dinon mein kuchh safaron mein dekha ke log sakht garmi ki wjah se apne hathon ko apne saron par rakh letey hain. aur ham mein se siwaey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abdullaah-bin-Rawaaha (Raziallahu anhu) ke, koi bhi roze-daar nahi tha."
2632,"Yahya-bin-Yahya , Malik , abi nazar , Umer , Maula Ibne-Abbas , Hazrat umme-al-fazal-binte-Haarisa se riwayat hai ke kuchh logon ne unke paas Arfa ke din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke rozey ke barey mein baat cheet ki unmein se kuchh ne kaha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rozey ki haalat mein they aur kuchh ne kaha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rozey ki haalat mein nahi they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf doodh ka aik piyala us waqt bheja jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne oont par Arfa ke din sawar they, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wo doodh pi liya."
2633,"Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim , ibne-abi-Umar , Sufiyan , Hazrat abi-ansar se isi sanad ke sath riwayat hai lekin usmein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka oont par Sawar honey ka zikr nahi."
2634,"Zuhair-bin-Harab , Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi , Sufiyan , Hazrat Saalim-bi-abi-nazar (Raziallahu anhu) se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah riwayat naql ki gaee hai."
2635,"Haroon-bin-Saeed, ibne-Wahab , Amr , abi-nazar , Maula-Ibne-Abbas , Hazrat umme-Fazal (Raziallahu anhu) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) mein se kuchh logon ne Arfa ke din roze ke barey mein shak kiya. Hazrat umme-Fazal (Raziallahu anhu) farmati hain ke ham bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they, to maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf aik piyala bheja jis mein doodh tha Arfa ke din to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wo doodh pi liya."
2636,"Haroon-bin-Saeed, ibne-Wahab , umr , Bukair-bin-Ashajj , Kureb , Maula Ibne-Abbas , Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi se riwayat hai wo farmati hain ke log Arfa ke din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke rozey ke barey mein shak mein pad gaey. chunanche Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf doodh ka aik lota bheja jis waqt ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Arafaat ke maidan mein khadey huey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se doodh piyaa jabke log Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf dekh rahe they."
2637,"Zuhair-bin-Harab , Jareer, Hisham-bin-Urwa , Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai farmati hain ke Quraish jahiliyat ke zamane mein aashoora ke din roza rakhtey they. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi jab Madina ki taraf hijrat farmai to apne sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ko bhi iska roza rakhney ka hukm farmaya to jab Ramazan ke rozey farz kar diye gaey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo chahey yaume-aashoora ka roza rakhey aur jo chahey chhod de."
2638,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , abu-Kuraib , ibne-Numair , Hazrat Hisham se isi sanad ke sath riwayat hai aur hadis ke shuru mein zikr nahi kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) yaume aashoora ka roza rakhtey they. aur hadis ke aakhir mein hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aashoora ka roza chhod diya ke jo chahey iska roza rakhey aur jo chahey chhod de. aur unhon-ne Jarir ki riwayat ki tarah , usko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke farman ka hissa qarar nahi diya."
2639,"Amr Naqid , Sufiyan , Zohri , Urwa , Sayeda Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke aashoora ke din jahiliyat ke zamane mein roza rakha jata tha to jab Islam aa gaya to ab jo chahey iska roza rakhey aur jo chahey chhod de."
2640,"Hurmala-bin-Yahya , ibne- Wahab , Yunus , ibne-Shahab , Urwa-bin-Zubair , Sayeda Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Ramazan ke rozey farz honey se pahley aashoora ke rozey ka hukm farmaya kartey they, to jab Ramazan ke rozey farz ho gaey to jo chahey aashoora ke din roza rakhey aur jo chahey chhod de."
2641,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed , Muhammad-bin-Rumeh , Lais-bin-Saeed, Yazeed-bin-abi-Habib , Urwa , Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke jahiliyat ke zamaney mein qureshi log aashoora ke din roza rakhney ka hukm saadir farmaya kartey they, to jab Ramazan ke rozey farz ho gaey to (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya ( jo chahey aashoora ke din roza rakhey aur jo chahey chhod de."
2642,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , Abdullah-bin-Numair , ibne-Numair , Ubaidullah , Naafe , Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke jahiliyat ke zamaney ke log aashoora ke din roza rakhtey they. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur musalmanon ne bhi Ramazan ke rozey farz honey se pahley iska roza rakha. jab Ramazan ke rozey farz ho gaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ''aashoora Allah ke dinon mein se aik din hai to jo chahey aashoora ka roza rakhey aur jo chahey usey chhod de.''"
2643,"Muhammad-bin-Musanna , Zuhair-bin-Harab , Yahya , abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , abu-Usama , Hazrat Ubaidullah se isi sanad ke sath bhi ye hadis riwayat ki gaee hai."
2644,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed , Leis , ibne- Rumeh , Leis , Naafe , Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aashoora ke din ka zikr kiya gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jahiliyat waley log us din roza rakhtey they, to tum mein jo koi pasand karta hai ke wo roza rakhey to rakh ley aur jo koi na-pasand karta hai to wo chhod de."
2645,"abu-Kuraib , abu-Usama , Waleed , ibne- Kasir , Naafe , Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aashoora ke din ke barey mein farmatey huey suna ke ye wo din hai jis din jahiliyat ke log roza rakhtey they. to jo koi pasand karta hai ke is din roza rakhey to wo roza rakh ley aur jo koi ye pasand karta hai ke chhod de to wo chhod de. aur Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) roza nahi rakhtey they siwaey iske ke un rozon se muwafiqat (barabari) ho jaey."
2646,"Muhammad-bin-Ahmed-bin-abi-Khalaf , Rooh , abu-Malik , Ubaidullah-bin-Akhnas , Naafe , Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aashoora ke din ke roza ka zikr kiya gaya phir aagey isi tarah hadis bayan ki."
2647,"Ahmed-bin-Usman-naufalii , abu-Aasim , Umar-bin-Muhammad-bin-Zaid asqalaanii , Saalim-bin-Abdullah , Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aashoora ke din ka zikr kiya gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye wo din hai ke jis din jahiliyat ke log roza rakhtey they, to jo chahey roza rakhey aur jo chahey roza chhod de."
2648,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , abu-Kuraib , abi-Muawiya , Abu-Bakar , abu-Muawia , Aamash , Umara , Hazrat Abdur-Rehman-bin-Yazeed farmatey hain ke Ash'as-bin-Qais Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein aaey us haal mein ke wo subah ka naashta kar rahe they. unhon-ne farmaya aey abu-Muhammad ! aao naashta kar lo to unhon-ne kaha ke kya aaj aashoora ka din nahi hai? Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke kya to janta hai ke aashoora ka din kya hai? Ash'as ne kaha wo kya hai? Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke ye wo din hai ke jis din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Ramazan ke mahiney ke rozey farz honey se pahley roza rakha kartey they. to jab Ramazan ke mahiney ke rozey farz ho gaey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aashoora ke din ka roza chhod diya."
2649,"Zuhair-bin-Harab , Usman-bin-abi-Sheba , Jareer, Hazrat Aamash se isi sanad ke sath ye hadis isi tarah naql ki gaee hai."
2650,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , Wakee , Yahya-bin-Saeed , Sufiyan , Muhammad-bin-Hatim , Zubeda Yami , Umara-bin-Umair , Hazrat Qais-bin-sakan (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Ash'as-bin-Qais aashoora ke din Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein us haal mein aaey ke aap kha rahe they. to unhon-ne farmaya aey abu-Muhammad ! qareeb ho jao aur khaao unhon-ne kaha, main rozey se hon Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke ham bhi is din roza rakhtey they lekin chhod diya."
2651,"Muhammad-bin-Hatim , Ishaq-bin-Mansur 'Israel' Mansoor , Ibrahim , Alqama , Ash'as-bin-Qais , Ali-ibne-Masood , Hazrat Alqama (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Ash'as-bin-Qais, ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aashoora ke, din us haal mein aaey ke wo khana kha rahe they, to unhon-ne farmaya ke aey abu-Abdur-Rehman ! aaj to aashoora hai? to ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke Ramazan ke rozey farz honey se pahley roza rakha jata tha to jab Ramazan ke rozey farz ho gaey ye roza chhod diya gaya, ke agar tera roza nahi to to bhi kha ."
2652,"Abu-Bakar-ibne-Abi-Sheba , Ubaidullah-bin-Musa , Sheban , Ash'as-bin-abi-Shasha , Jafar-bin-abi-Sour , Hazrat Jaabir-bin-samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aashoora ke din roza rakhney ka hukm farmatey they aur hamein is par aamada kartey they aur iska ehtimaam kartey they, to jab Ramazan ke rozey farz kar diye gaey to phir aap na hamein iska hukm farmatey aur na us se mana farmatey aur na hi uska ehtimaam farmatey."
2653,"Hurmala-bin-Yahya , ibne- Wahab , Yunus , ibne-Shahab , Hazrat Humaid-bin-Abdur-Rehman , khabar detey hain ke unhon-ne Hazrat Muawiya-bin-abi-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) ka Madina mein khutba suna yani jab wo Madina aaey to unhon-ne aashoora ke din khutba diya aur farmaya aey Madina waalo! kahan hain tumharey ulma ? maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko us din ke liye farmatey huey suna ke ye aashoora ka din hai aur Allah Taala ne tum par is din ka roza farz nahi kiya aur main rozey se hon to jo tum mein se pasand karta ho ke wo roza rakhey to usey chahiye ke wo roza rakh ley aur jo tum mein se pasand karta ho ke wo iftaar kar ley to usey chahiye ke wo iftaar kar ley."
2654,"abu-Taahir-Abdullah , Abdullah-bin-Wahab , Malik-bin-Anas , ibne-Shahab se isi sanad ke sath mazkura (uper zikr) hadis ki tarah riwayat kiya gaya hai."
2655,"ibne-abi-Umar , Sufiyan-bin-Uena, Hazrat Zohri se isi sanad ke sath riwayat hai ke unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us din ke barey mein farmatey huey suna ke main rozey se hon ke jo chahta hai ke roza rakh ley wo rakh ley aur Malik-bin-Anas aur Yunus ki hadis ka baqi hissey zikr nahi kiya."
2656,"Yahya-bin-Yahya , Hushaim-abi-Bishr , Saeed-bin-Jubair , Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina tashrif laey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yahudiyon ko aashoora ke din roza rakhtey huey paya to logon ne unse is rozey ke barey mein puchha to wo kehney lagey ke ye wo din hai ke jis mein Allah Taala ne Hazrat Musa (Alaihissalam) ko aur Bani-Israeel ko firaun par ghalba ata farmaya tha, to ham us din ki azmat ki wjah se roza rakhtey hain. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ham tum se zyada Hazrat Musa (Alaihissalam) ke qareeb hain to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is rozey ka hukm farmaya."
2657,"ibne-Bashar , Abu-Bakar-bin-Naafe , Muhammad-bin-Jafar , Shoba , abi-Bishr isi sanad ke sath abi-Bishr se isi tarah riwayat naql ki gaee hai aur is mein hai ke aap ne unse uski wjah poochhi."
2658,"ibne-abi-Umar , Sufiyan , Ayub , Abdullah-bin Saeed-bin-Jubair , Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Madina tashrif laey to aap ne yahudiyon ko aashoora ke din roza rakhtey huey paya, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke is din ki kya wjah hai? to wo kehney lagey ke ye wo azeem din hai ke jis mein Allah Taala ne Musa (Alaihissalam) aur unki qaum ko nijat ata farmai aur firaun aur uski qaum ko gharq farmaya. chunanche Hazrat Musa (Alaihissalam) ne shukraaney ka roza rakha isliye ham bhi roza rakhtey hain, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ham zyada haq daar hain aur tum se zyada Musa (Alaihissalam) ke qareeb hain to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi aashoora ke din roza rakha aur apne sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ko bhi roza rakhney ka hukm farmaya."
2659,"Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim , Abdur-Razzaq , Mamar , Ayub se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah riwayat naql ki gaee hai siwaey iske ke usmein ibne- Saeed-bin-Jubair ka naam zikr nahi kiya gaya."
2660,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , ibne-Numair , abu-Usama , abi-Umais , Qais-bin-Saalim , taariq-bin-shahaab , Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, farmaya ke Yahudi log aashoora ke din ki ta'zeem kartey they aur usey eid samajhtey they, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya : ''tum bhi us din ko roza rakho.''"
2661,"Ahmed-bin-munzir , Hammad-bin-Usaama , abu-Umais , Qais , sadqa-bin-abi-Imran , Qais-bin-Saalim , taariq-bin-shahaab , hazrat-abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai farmatey hain ke khaibar ke Yahudi aashoora ke din roza rakhtey they aur usey eid samajhtey they. aur apni aurton ko zewar pahnaatey aur banao singhaar kartey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum bhi is din ko roza rakho."
2662,"Abu-Bakar-ibne- Sheba , Amr-naaqid , Sufiyan , Abu-Bakar , ibne-Uena , Ubaidullah-ibne-abi-Yazeed , hazrat-Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aashoora ke din ke rozon ke barey mein puchha gaya to unhon-ne farmaya ke main nahi janta ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us aashoora ke din ke ilawa kisi aur din ki wjah se roza rakha ho aur na kisi mahiney mein siwaey us mahiney yani Ramazan ke."
2663,"Muhammad-bin-Raafe , Abdur-Razzaq , ibne-Juraij , Ubaidullah-bin-abi-Yazeed isi sanad ke sath isi tarah ki ye hadis naql ki gaee hai."
2664,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , Wakee-bin-Jarraah , haajib-ibne-Umar , Hazrat Hakam-bin-Aaraj se riwayat hai farmatey hain ke main Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaya us haal mein ke wo zam-zam (ke qareeb ( apni chadar se tek lagaey baithey they, to maine unse arz kiya ke mujhey aashoorey ke rozey ke barey mein khabar dijiye. unhon-ne farmaya ke jab to muharram ka chaand dekhey to gintaa reh. aur naween taareekh ke din ki subah rozey ki haalat mein kar. maine arz kiya ke kya Muhammad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) isi tarah roza rakhtey they unhon-ne farmaya haan !"
2665,"Muhammad-bin-Hatim , Yahya-bin-Saeed , Muawiya-bin-Amr , hazrat-Hakam-bin-Aaraj kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se us haal mein ke wo zam-zam ke paas apni chadar se tek lagaey baithey they aashoora ke rozey ke barey mein puchha iske baad isi tarah hadis mubaraka hai."
2666,"Hasan-bin-Ali Hulwani , ibne-abi-Maryam , Yahya-bin-Ayub , Ismail-bin-Umayya , Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain : ke jis waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aashoora ke din roza rakha aur uske rozey ka hukm farmaya to unhon-ne arz kiya : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! us din to Yahudi aur nasara ta'zeem kartey hain to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab aainda saal aayega to ham naween taareekh ka bhi roza rakhengey. rawi ne kaha ke abhi aainda saal nahi aaya tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wafat pa gaey."
2667,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , abu-Kuraib , Wakee , ibne-abi-Ze'ib , Qasim-bin-Abbas , Abdullah-bin-Umair , Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar main aaney waley saal tak zinda raha to main naween taareekh ka bhi zaroor roza rakhoonga aur Abu-Bakar ki riwayat mein hai ke aap ne farmaya aashoora ke din ka roza ."
2668,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed , Hatim yani ibne- Ismail , Yazeed-bin-abi-Ubaid , Hazrat Salma-bin-Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhon-ne farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qabila Aslam ke aik aadmi ko aashoora ke din bheja aur usey hukm farmaya ke wo logon mein elaan kar de ke jis aadmi ne roza na rakha ho wo roza rakh ley. aur jisne kha liya ho to usey chahiye ke wo apne rozey ko raat tak pura kar ley."
2669,"Abu-Bakar-bin-Naafe , Bishr-bin-Mufazzal-bin-laahiq , Khalid-bin-Zakwaan, Hazrat Rabe-binte-muawwiz-bin-ifraa (Raziallahu anhu) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aashoora ki subah ko Ansar ki us basti ki taraf jo Madina Munawra ke ird-gird thi ye paigham bhijwa diya ke jis aadmi ne subah roza rakha to wo apne rozey ko pura kar ley aur jisne subah ko iftaar kar liya ho to usey chahiye ke baqi din roza pura kar ley iske baad ham roza rakhtey they aur ham apne chhotey bachchon ko bhi roza rakhwaatey they aur ham unhein masjid ki taraf ley jatey aur ham unke liye rooii ki gudiye banatey aur jab un bachchon mein se koi khaney ki wjah se rotaa to ham unhein wo gudiya de detey taake wo iftaarii tak unke sath kheltey rahen."
2670,"Yahya-bin-Yahya , abu-ma'shar , attaar , Hazrat Khalid-bin Zakwan kehtey hain ke maine Rabe-binte-muawwiz (Raziallahu anhu) se aashoora ke rozey ke barey mein puchha to unhon-ne farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ansar ki basti mein apna numaainda bheja phir aagey Bishr ki hadis ki tarah riwayat zikr ki siwaey iske ke unhon-ne kaha ke ham un bachchon ke liye rooii ki gudiya banatey taake wo unse khelein. aur wo hamarey sath masjid mein jatey to jab wo ham se khana maangtey to ham unhein wo gudiya de detey aur wo unse khel mein lag kar roza bhool jatey yahan tak ke unka roza pura ho jata."
2671,"Yahya-bin-Yahya, Malik ibne-Shahab, Hazrat abu Ubaid Maula ibne-Azhar se riwayat hai unhon-ne kaha ke main eid ke din Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas maujood tha to aap aaey aur Namaz padhi phir Namaz se farigh ho kar logon ko khutba diya aur farmaya ke ye wo din hain jis main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne roza rakhney se mana farmaya hai aik wo din hai ke jis din tum iftaar kartey ho aur doosra wo din hai ke jis main tum apni qurbaniyon ka gosht khaatey ho."
2672,"Yahya-bin-Yahya, Malik, Muhammad-bin-Yahya ibne- hibban, Aaraj , Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 dinon ke rozon se mana farmaya aik qurbani ke din aur doosra fitr ke din ."
2673,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed , Jareer, Abdul-Malik , ibne- Umer , Qaza , Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke maine aik hadis suni jo mujhey badi ajeeb lagi Qaza kehtey hain ke maine abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha, kya aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye hadis suni hai? Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) kaha ke kya main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wo baat keh sakta hun jis ko maine aap se na suna ho unhon-ne farmaya ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna ke 2 dinon mein roza rakhna durust nahi aik qurbani ke din doosrey ( Ramazan ( eidul-fitr ke din ."
2674,"abu-Kamil Jahdari , Abdul-Azeez bin Mukhtar , Amr-bin-Yahya, Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 dinon ke rozey rakhney se mana farmaya hai aik eidul-fitr ke din doosrey eidul-azha yani qurbani ke din ."
2675,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , Wakee Ibne-Aun , Hazrat Ziyad bin Juber se riwayat hai ke farmaya ke aik aadmi Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf aaya aur arz kya ke maine mannat maana thi ke main aik din ka roza rakhunga to wo din qurbani ke eid ke din ya eidul-fitr ke din se muwafiqat kar raha hai to Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala ne mannat ko pura karne ka hukm diya hai aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us din ke rozey se mana farmaya hai."
2676,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 rozon , fitr ke din aur qurbani ke din (ke rozon ( se mana farmaya hai."
2677,"Suraij-bin-Yoonus , Hushaim , Khalid , abi-Maleeh, Hazrat Nabeesha (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tashreeq ke din khaney aur peeney ke din hain."
2678,"Muhammad-bin-Abdullah ibne-Numair , Ismail ibne-Ulaih , Khalid , abi-Maleeh , nabeesha , isi sanad ke sath bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi hadis ki tarah hadis manqul hai aur is mein sirf zikrullah ke alfaz zayed hain."
2679,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , Muhammad-bin-Sabiq, Ibrahim bin Tehman , abi Zuber , ibne- Kab-bin-Malik apne bap se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein aur Aus bin Hadsan (Raziallahu anhu) ko tashreeq ke dinon mein ye elaan karaaney ke liye bheja ke jannat mein momin ke siwa koi dakhil nahi hoga aur Mina ke din khaney aur peeney ke din hain."
2680,"abd bin Humaid , abu-Aamir , Abdul-Malik bin-Amr , Ibrahim bin Tehman isi sanad ke sath bhi isi tarah riwayat naql ki gaee hai siwaey iske ke usmein hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum donon ja kar elaan kar do."
2681,"Amr Naqid , Sufiyan-bin-Uena, Abdul-Hameed ibne- Juber, Muhammad-bin Ibad bin Jafar kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha is haal mein ke wo Baitullah ka tawaaf kar rahe they ke kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Juma ke din roza rakhney se mana farmaya hai? to unhon-ne farmaya haan ! qism hai us ghar ke rab ki."
2682,"Muhammad-bin Raafe , Abdur-Razzaq , ibne-Juraij , abdul-Hameed bin Juber bin Sheba , Muhammad-bin Ibad Jafar , Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) is sanad mein bhi Muhammad-bin Ibad bin Jafar khabar detey hain ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se is hadis ki tarah naql farmaya."
2683,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , Hafs , abu-Muawiya , Aamash , Yahya-bin-Yahya , abu-Muawiya , Aamash , abi Saleh , Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya tum mein se koi aadmi Juma ke din roza na rakhey siwaey iske ke wo us se pahley ya uske baad roza rakhey ."
2684,"abu-Kuraib, Husain yani Jau'fi, Zayda, Hisham , Ibne-Sirin , Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke raaton mein se Juma ki raat ko qiyam ke sath makhsoos na karo aur na hi dinon mein se Juma ke din ko rozey ke sath makhsoos karo siwaey iske ke tum mein se jo koi rozey rakh raha ho."
2685,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed, Bakr yani ibne- Muzar , Amr-bin-Haris , Bukair , Yazeed Maula Salma , Hazrat Salma-bin-Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke jab ye aayate-karima nazil hui. ( وَعَلَى الَّذِينَ يُطِيقُونَہ فِدْيَۃٌ طَعَامُ مِسْكِينٍ (aur jo log roza rakhney ki taqat rakhtey hon lekin rakhey nahi, wo roze ke badle mein aik miskeen ko khana khila dein jis aadmi ka roza chhodney ka irada hota to wo fidya de deta yahan tak ke iske baad wali aayat nazil hui jisne us hukm ko mansookh kar diya."
2686,"Amr bin sawwad Aamiri , Abdullah-bin Wahab , Amr-bin-Haris Bukair bin ashja, Yazeed Maula Salma bin Akwa, Hazrat Salma-bin-Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai farmatey hain ke Ramazan ke mahine mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein ham se jo chahta roza rakh leta aur jo chahta roza chhod deta aur aik miskeen ko khana khula kar aik rozey ka fidya de deta yahan tak ke ye aayate-kareema nazil hui ( فَمَن شَهِدَ مِنكُمُ الشَّهْرَ‌فَلْيَصُمْهُ ( to jo tum mein se is maheene mein maujood ho to usey chahiye ke wo roza rakhey ."
2687,"Ahmed bin-Abdullah-bin Yunus , Zuhair , Yahya-bin-Saeed , Hazrat abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai farmatey hain. ke maine Hazrat Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) ko farmatey huey suna ke Ramazan ke rozey mujh se qaza ho jatey they, to main un rozon ki siwaey Shoban mein qaza nahi kar sakti thi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein mashghooliyat ki wjah se."
2688,"Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim, Bishr-bin-Umar Zahrani , Sulaiman-bin Bilal, Yahya-bin-Saeed isi sanad ke sath isi tarah bayan kartey hain siwaey iske usmein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wjah se mashghool rehti thi."
2689,"Muhammad-bin Raafe , Abdur-Razzaq , ibne-Juraij , Yahya-bin-Saeed , ne is sanad ke sath is tarah bayan kya ke mera khayal hai ke ye taakheer Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein mashghooliyat ki wjah se hoti thi. ye baat Yahya kehtey hain"
2690,"Muhammad-bin-Musanna , abdul-Wahab, Amr Naqid, Sufiyan, Hazrat Yahya se is sanad ke sath riwayat hai aur is hadis mein ye zikr nahi kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wjah se qaza mein takheer hoti thi."
2691,"Muhammad-bin abi umr Makki, Abdul-Azeez bin-Muhammad Darawardi, Yazeed bin-Abdullah-bin haad, Muhammad-bin Ibrahim, abi Salma bin Abdur-Rehman, Sayeda Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai farmati hain ke agar ham mein se koi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein koi roza chhodti thi to wo qudrat na rakhti ke unki qaza kar ley Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wjah se yahan tak ke Shoban aa jata."
2692,"Harun bin Saeed, Ahmed bin Esa , ibne- Wahab, Amr-bin-Haaris , Ubaidullah bin abi Jafar , Muhammad-bin-Jafar bin Zuber , Urwa , Sayeda Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo aadmi intiqal kar jaey aur is par kuchh rozey lazim hon to uska waaris uski taraf se rozey rakhey ."
2693,"Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim , Esa-bin-Yonus , Aamash , Muslim , Saeed-bin-Jubair , Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke aik aurat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aai aur kehney lagi ke meri maan ka intiqal ho gaya hai aur is par aik mahiney ke rozey lazim hain to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tera kya khayal hai ke agar is par koi qarz hota to kya to usey ada karti ? us ne arz kya haan ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala ke qarz ka zyada haq hai ke usey ada kya jaey."
2694,"Ahmed bin umr Wakie, Husain bin Ali , Zayda , Sulaiman , Muslim , Saeed-bin-Jubair , Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke aik aadmi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur us ne arz kya aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! meri maan ka intiqal ho gaya hai aur is par aik mahiney ke rozon ki qaza lazim hai. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar teri maan par koi qarz hota to kya to wo qarz uski taraf se ada karta ? arz kya ke haan! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah ka qarz zyada iska haqdar hai ke usey ada kya jaey. Sulaiman ne kaha : Hakam aur Salma bin kuheil donon ne kaha ke jab muslim) البطین ( ne ye hadis sunai thi ham bhi baithey huey they, donon ne kaha : ham ne Mujahid se bhi suna, wo ye hadis Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kar rahe they."
2695,"abu-Saeed Ashajj , abu-Khalid , Aamash , Salma bin kuheil , Hakam-bin-Utaiba , Muslim , Saeed-bin-Jubair , Mujahid , ata , Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) is sanad ke sath Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us hadis ki tarah riwayat kya."
2696,"Ishaq-bin-Mansur, ibne-abi Khalaf , abd bin Humaid , Zakariya-bin Adi , Ubaidullaah-bin-Amr , Zaid-bin-abi-Unaisa , Hakam-bin-Utaiba , Saeed-bin-Jubair , Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai farmaya ke aik aurat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aai aur arz karne lagi aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) meri maan ka intiqal ho gaya hai is par mannat ka roza lazim tha to kya main uski taraf se roza rakhoon ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tera kya khayal hai? ke agar teri maan par koi qarz hota to kya to uski taraf se ada karti ? us ne arz kya haan ! aap ne farmaya ke Allah ka qarz is baat ka zyada haq daar hai ke usey ada kya jaey aap ne farmaya ke to apni maa ki taraf se roza rakh."
2697,"Ali-bin-Mus-hir , abul-Hasan ne Abdullah-bin ata se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin Barida se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, kaha : aik baar main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas betha hua tha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aa kar aik aurat ne kaha : maine apni walida ko aik londi bataur sadqa di thi aur wo ( walida ( faut ho gaee hain, kaha : to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tumhara ajr pakka ho gaya aur virasat ne wo ( londi ( tumhen lota di. us ne puchha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! unke zimmey aik maah ke rozey they, kya main unki taraf se rozey rakhun ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum unki taraf se rozey rakho . us ne puchha : unhon-ne kabhi Haj nahi kya tha, kya main unki taraf se Haj karun? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum unki taraf se Haj karo."
2698,"Abdullah-bin-Numair ne Abdullah-bin ata se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin Barida se, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas betha hua tha. padhi. ( aagey ( ibne-Mus-hir ki hadis ki tarah ( hadis bayan ki) magar unhon-ne kaha : 2 maah ke rozey ."
2699,"Abdur-Razzaq ne kaha : hamein ( Sufiyan ( Sory ne Abdullah-bin Ata se khabar di, unhon-ne ibne-bareeda se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, kaha : aik aurat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui. iske baad usi (pichhli hadis) ki tarah hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne kaha : aik maah ke rozey ."
2700,Ubaidullah bin-Musa ne Sufiyan ( Sory ( se isi sanad ke sath (pichhli hadis ki manind (tarah) ( hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne kaha : 2 maah ke rozey .
2701,"Abdul-Malik bin abi Sulaiman ne Abdullah-bin-Ata se, unhon-ne Sulaiman-bin-Buraida se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aik aurat aai. padhi.  ( aagey ( unki hadis ki tarah ( bayan kya (aur unhon-ne bhi kaha : aik maah ke rozey ."
2702,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se kisi ko khaney ki taraf bulaya jaey aur wo roze-daar ho to wo keh de : main rozey se hun.
2703,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne (Nabi Karim se) riwayat ki, kaha : jab tum mein se koi kisi din rozey se ho to wo fahash (gandi) baat bolney se bachey, na jahaalat wala koi kaam karey, agar koi shakhs us se gaali-galoch ya ladai jhagdaa ( karna ( chahey to wo kahey : main roze-daar hun, main roze-daar hun."
2704,"ibne-Shahab se riwayat hai, kaha : Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne mujhey bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kehtey huey suna, izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne farmaya : ibne-Aadam ke tamam aamaal uske liye hain siwaey rozey ke , wo mere liye hai aur main hi uski jaza dunga. us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki jaan hai ! roze-daar ke munh ki bo Allah ke nazdeek kastoori ki khushbu se zyada pasandida hai."
2705,"Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : roza aik dhaal hai."
2706,"Ata ne Abu-Saleh Zayyat se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne farmaya : ibne-Aadam ka har amal uske liye hai siwaey rozey ke , wo mere liye hai aur main hi uski jaza doonga aur roza dhaal hai lihaza jab tum mein se kisi ke rozey ka din ho to wo us din fahash baat na karey aur na shor w ghul kare. agar koi usey bura bhala kahey ya us se jhagdaa karey to wo keh de : main roze-daar hun, main roze-daar hun. us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki jaan hai ! qiyamat ke din roze-daar ke munh ki bo Allah ke nazdeek kastoori ki khushbu se bhi zyada pasandida hogi aur roze-daar ke liye 2 khushi ke mauqe hain wo un donon par khush hota hai : jab wo ( roza ( iftaar karta hai to apne iftaar se khush hota hai aur jab apne rab ko milega to apne rozey (ki wjah ( se khush hoga."
2707,"Aamash ne Abu-Saleh se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ibne-Aadam ka har amal badhaya jata hai. neki das guna se saat so guna tak (badha di jati hai) Allah Taala ne farmaya : siwaey rozey ke (kyonke) wo ( khaalisatan ( mere liye hai aur main hi uski jaza dunga . wo meri khaatir apni khahish aur apna khana peena chhod deta hai. roze-daar ke liye 2 khushiyan hain aik khushi uske ( roza ( iftaar karne ke waqt ki aur (doosri ( khushi apne rab se mulaqat ke waqt ki. roze-daar ke munh ki bo Allah ke nazdeek kastoori ki khushbu se bhi zyada pasandida hai."
2708,"Muhammad-bin-Fuzail ne abu Sanan se, unhon-ne Abu-Saleh se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) aur Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, un donon ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : izzat aur jalaal waala Allah farmata hai: bila shubah roza mere liye hai aur main hi uski jaza dunga. bila shubah roze-daar ke liye 2 khushiyan hain : jab wo ( roza ( iftaar karta hai khush hota hai. aur jab wo Allah se mulaqat karega . khush hoga, aur us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki jaan hai ! Allah ke yahan , roze-daar ke munh ki bo kastoori ki khushbu se bhi zyada pasandida hai."
2709,"Abdul-Azeez bin Muslim ne kaha : hamein Zirar bin Murra ( abu-Sanaan ( ne isi sanad ke sath (pichhli hadis ki tarah ( hadis sunai, kaha : aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab wo Allah se milega aur Allah usko ajr w sawab ata karega to wo khush hoga."
2710,"Hazrat Sahal-bin-Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jannat mein aik (aisa) darwaza hai jisey Rayyan kaha jata hai qiyamat ke din usmein se roze-daar dakhil hongey unke sath unke siwa koi aur dakhil nahi hoga. jab unmein se aakhiri ( fard ( dakhil ho jaeyga to wo ( darwaza band kar diya jaeyga, iske baad koi us se dakhil nahi ho sakega."
2711,"ibne-Haad ne Suhel bin abi Saleh se, unhon-ne Nauman bin abi Ayash se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya koi shakhs nahi jo Allah ki raah mein aik din ka roza rakhey magar Allah Taala us din (ke rozey ( badley iske chehrey ko (jahannam ki) aag se 70 saal ki masafat tak door kar dega."
2712,"Abdul-Azeez yani darawardi ne Suhel se isi sanad ke sath , (pichhli hadis ki tarah ( hadis bayan ki,"
2713,"ibne-Juraij ne Yahya-bin-Saeed aur Suhel bin abi Saleh se khabar di ke un donon ne Nauman bin Ayash Zarqi se khabar di ke , wo Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kar rahe they. kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : jisne Allah ki raah mein aik din ka roza rakha Allah Taala uske chehrey ko (jahannam ki) aag se 70 saal ki masafat tak door kar deta hai."
2714,"abdul-Wahid bin Ziyad ne hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein Talha bin Yahya ne hadis sunai, ( unhon-ne kaha : ( mujhey Aaisha binte- Talha ne Ummul-Momenin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se hadis sunai, kaha : aik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : aey Aaisha ! kya tumharey paas ( khaney ki) koi cheez hai? kaha : to maine kaha ! aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! hamarey paas koi cheez nahi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : to ( phir ( main rozey se hun. iske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar tashrif le gaey to hamarey paas hadiya bheja gaya ya hamarey paas mulaqati (jo hadiya laey ( aa gaey. kaha : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wapas tashrif laaey, maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! hamein hadiya diya gaya hai. ya hamarey paas mehman aaey aur maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye kuchh mehfooz karke rakha hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo kya hai? maine kaha : wo Hees ( khajoor , ghi aur paneer se bana hua khana ( hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usey laaiye to main usey ley aai aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey kha liya, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine rozey ki haalat mein subah ki thi. Talha ne kaha : maine ye hadis Mujahid ko sunai to unhon-ne kaha : ye us aadmi ki tarah hai jo apne maal se sadqa nikaalta hai, agar wo chahey to de dey aur agar wo chahey to usko rok ley."
2715,"Wakee ne baqi bachi pichhli sanad ke sath Ummul-Momenin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : aik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere paas tashrif laey aur puchha : kya aap logon ke paas ( khaney ki) koi cheez hai? to ham ne kaha : nahi, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : to phir main rozey se hun. phir aik aur din Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey to ham ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! hamein hees tohfey mein mila hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mujhey khilaiye , maine rozey ki haalat mein subah ki thi. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kha liya."
2716,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs rozey ki haalat mein bhool gaya aur kha liya ya pi liya to wo apna roza pura karey kyonke usko Allah ne khilaya aur pilaya hai."
2717,"Saeed Jurairi ne Abdullah-bin Shaqiq se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se malum kya : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Ramazan ke siwa kisi mutaiyan mahiney ke rozey rakhtey they? unhon-ne jawab diya : Allah ki qism ! Ramazan ke siwa Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kisi mutaiyan mahiney ke) poorey ( rozey nahi rakhey yahan tak ke aap aagey tashrif le gaey aur na Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kisi mahiney ke rozey tark kiye, jab tak ke usmein se ( kuchh dinon ke) rozey rakh ( na ( liye."
2718,"Kahmas ne Abdullah-bin Shaqiq se hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kisi poorey mahiney ke rozey rakhtey they? unhon-ne jawab diya : main nahi janti ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ramazan ke siwa kisi mahiney ke poorey rozey rakhey hon aur na Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne poorey mahiney ke rozey chhodey . yahan tak ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usmein se ( kuchh dinon ke) rozey rakh ( na ( letey , yahan tak ke aap apni (hamesha ki manzil ki) raah par tashrif ley gaey."
2719,"Hammad ne Ayub aur Hisham se, unhon-ne Muhammad se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin Shaqiq se riwayat ki. Hammad ne kaha : mera khayal hai, Ayub ne us hadis ko Abdullah-bin Shaqiq se suna. kaha : maine Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke rozon ke barey mein malum kya to unhon-ne kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rozey rakhtey they yahan tak ke ham kehtey : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rozey par rozey rakhtey ja rahe hain. aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) iftaar kartey ( rozey rakhna tark kar detey ( yahan tak ke ham kehtey : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) musalsal iftaar kar rahe hain, kaha : jab se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina tashrif laey hain, maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko nahi dekha ke aap ne kisi poorey mahiney ke rozey rakhey hon, iske siwa ke wo Ramazan ka mahina ho."
2720,"Quteba ne hamein hadis sunai, (kaha : ( hamein Hammad ne Ayub se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin Shaqiq se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se sawal kya. padhi. usi (pichhli hadis) ki tarah , unhon-ne sanad mein Hisham aur Muhammad ka zikr nahi kya."
2721,"Umar-bin Ubaidullah ke aazad karda ghulam abu-Nazar ne abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman (bin Auf ( se aur unhon-ne Ummul-Momenin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rozey rakhtey yahan tak ke ham kehtey : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rozey tark nahi karengey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rozey chhod detey yahan tak ke ham kehtey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rozey nahi rakhengey, aur maine dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ramazan ke siwa kabhi kisi mahiney ke poorey rozey rakhey hon, aur maine nahi dekha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kisi (aur ( mahiney mein us se zyada rozey rakhey hon jitney Shoban mein rakhtey they."
2722,"ibne-abi Labid ne abu-Salma se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke rozon ke barey mein puchha to unhon-ne bataya : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) musalsal rozey rakhtey yahan tak ke ham kehtey : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rozey tark nahi karengey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rozey chhod detey yahan tak ke ham kehtey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rozey nahi rakhengey, aur maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kisi aur mahiney mein Shoban ke rozon ki nisbat zyada rozey rakhtey nahi dekha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (maano) poorey Shoban ke rozey rakhtey they, mahz chand din chhod kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) pura Shoban rozey rakhtey they."
2723,"Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir ne abu-Salma se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, aur kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) saal ke kisi mahiney mein, Shoban se badh kar, rozey nahi rakhtey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmaya kartey they : itney hi aamaal apnao jitnon ki tum taqat rakhtey ho. kyonke Allah Taala hargiz nahi uktaeyga yahan tak ke tum khud hi (amal karne se) ukta jaogey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmaya kartey they : Allah ke yahan sabse zyada pasandida amal wo hai jis par amal karne wala hamesha qaaim rahe chahey wo thoda hi kyon na ho."
2724,"abu-Awana ne abu Bishr se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Jubair se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ramazan ke siwa kabhi pura mahina rozey nahi rakhey . jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rozey rakhtey to itney rozey rakhtey ke kehney wala kehta : nahi, Allah ki qism ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rozey tark nahi karengey aur jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rozey chhodtey to (musalsal ( chhodtey yahan tak ke kehney wala kehta : nahi, Allah ki qism ! aap rozey nahi rakhengey ."
2725,Shoba ne isi sanad ke sath abu Bishr se (pichhli hadis ki tarah) riwayat ki aur) pura mahina ke bajaey) jab se Madina aaey mutwaatir koi mahina kaha.
2726,"Abdullah-bin-Numair ne kaha : hamein Usman bin-Hakim ne hadis sunai, kaha : maine Saeed-bin-Jubair se rajab mein roza rakhney ke barey mein sawal kya, aur ham un dinon rajab main hi they, to unhon-ne kaha : maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye farmatey huey suna : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rozey rakhtey yahan tak ke ham kehtey : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rozey tark nahi karengey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rozey tark kartey yahan tak ke ham kehtey : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rozey nahi rakhengey ."
2727,Ali-bin-Mus-hir aur Esa-bin-Yonus donon ne isi sanad ke sath Usman bin-Hakim se usi (pichhli hadis) ki tarah riwayat ki.
2728,"Zuhair-bin-Harab aur Abu-Bakar bin Naafe ne. alfaz unhi ke hain. 2 alag alag sanadon ke sath Hammad se hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Sabit ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rozey rakhtey yahan tak ke kaha jata : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rozey shuru kar diye, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rozey shuru kar diye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rozey tark kartey yahan tak ke kaha jata : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rozey rakhney chhod diye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rozey rakhney chhod diye."
2729,"ibne-Shahab ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab aur abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Abdullah-bin Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko itlaa di gaee ke wo ( Abdullah ( kehta hai : main jab tak zinda hun (musalsal (raat ka qiyam karunga aur din ka roza rakhunga . to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum hi ho jo ye baatein kartey ho? maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! waqei maine hi ye kaha hai. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum ye kaam nahi kar sakogey, lihaza roza rakho aur roza tark bhi karo. neend bhi karo aur qiyam bhi karo, mahiney mein teen din ke rozey rakh liya karo kyonke har neki (ka ajr ( das guna hai. is tarah ye sarey waqt ke rozon ki tarah hai. maine kaha : main us se afzal amal ki taqat rakhta hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik din roza rakho aur 2 din na rakho . kaha : maine kaha : main us se afzal amal ki taqat rakhta hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik din roza rakho aur aik din na rakho . ye Dawud (Alaihissalam) ka roza hai. aur ye rozon ka sabse munsifana ( tariqa ( hai. kaha : main us se afzal amal ki taqat rakhta hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is se afzal koi sura nahi. Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ye baat mujhey apne ahal w ayaal se bhi Ziyad azeez hai ke main ( mahiney mein) teen dinon ki baat taslim kar leta jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmai thi."
2730,"Ikrima bin Ammar ne kaha : hamein Yahya ne hadis sunai kaha : main aur Abdullah-bin Yazeed Hazrat abu-Salma ke paas haziri ke liye (apne gharon se) rawana huey. ham ne aik paigham ley janey wala aadmi unke paas bheja to wo bhi hamarey liye bahar nikal aaey. wahan unke ghar ke darwazey ke paas aik masjid thi, kaha : ham masjid mein rahe yahan tak ke wo bhi hamarey paas aa gaey. unhon-ne kaha : agar tum chaho to ( ghar mein) dakhil ho jao aur agar chaho to yahin (masjid mein) baith jao . kaha : ham ne kaha : nahi, ham yahin baithengey , aap hamein hadis sunain . unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Hazrat Abdullah-bin Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis sunai, kaha : main musalsal rozey rakhta tha aur har raat ( qiyam mein poorey ( Quran ki qirat karta tha. Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney mera zikr kya gaya (aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey (ya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey paigham bheja aur main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : kya mujhey nahi bataya gaya ke tum hamesha (har roz ( roza rakhtey ho aur har raat ( pura ( Quran padhtey ho? maine kaha : aey Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! kyon nahi (ye baat durust hai) aur aisa karne mein mere peshe-nazar bhalai ke siwa kuchh nahi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tumharey liye itna hi kafi hai ke tum har mahiney mein teen din rozey rakho . maine kaha : aey Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! main is se afzal amal karne ki taqat rakhta hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum par tumhari biwi ka haq hai, tum par tumharey mahmanon ka haq hai, aur tum par tumharey jism ka haq hai, ( aakhir mein) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah ke Nabi Dawud (Alaihissalam) ke rozon ki tarah rozey rakho wo sab logon se badh kar ibadat guzaar they. kaha : maine kaha : aey Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! Dawud (Alaihissalam) ka roza kya tha? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo aik din roza rakhtey they aur aik din iftaar kartey they. farmaya : Quran ki qirat aik maah mein) mukammal kya ( karo. kaha : maine kaha : aey Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! main is se afzal amal ki taqat rakhta hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, usey har bees din mein padh liya karo. kaha : maine kaha : aey Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! main is se afzal amal ki taqat rakhta hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, usey har das din mein padh liya karo. kaha : maine kaha : aey Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! main is se afzal amal ki taqat rakhta hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, usey har saat (7) din mein padh liya karo. is se zyada na karo tum par tumhari biwi ka haq hai, tum par tumharey mahmaanon ka haq hai, aur tum par tumharey jism ka haq hai, kaha : maine (apne uper ( sakhti ki to mujh par sakhti ki gaee aur Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : tum nahi jantey shayad tumhari umr lambi ho. kaha : main usi ki taraf aa gaya jo mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bataya tha, jab main boodha ho gaya to maine pasand kya (aur tamanna ki) ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki rukhsat qabool kar li hoti ."
2731,"Husain al-Muallim ne Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se isi sanad ke sath (pichhli hadis ki tarah ( hadis sunai, aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke farman : har mahiney mein teen din ke baad ye alfaz zayed bayan kiye : tumharey liye har neki ke badley mein us jaisi das ( nekiyan ( hain. to ye sarey saal ke) rozey ( hain. aur (is ( hadis mein kaha : maine kaha : Allah ke Nabi Dawud (Alaihissalam) ka roza kya tha? farmaya : aadha saal aur unhon-ne hadis mein Quran padhney ke hawale se kuchh bayan nahi kya aur unhon-ne : tumharey mehmanon ka tum par haq hai ke alfaz bayan nahi kiye, uski bajaey unhon-ne kaha : (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (aur tumhari aulad ka tum par haq hai."
2732,"Sheban ne Yahya se, unhon-ne banu- zohra ke Maula Muhammad-bin Abdur-Rehman se, unhon-ne abu-Salma se riwayat ki. ( Yahya ne kaha : ( mera apne barey mein khayal hai ke maine khud bhi ye hadis abu-Salma se suni , unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : Quran Majeed ki tilawat mahiney main ( mukammal ( kya karo. maine kaha : main (is se zyada ki) quwwat paata hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bees raaton mein padh liya karo. maine kaha : main (is se zyada ki) quwwat paata hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : saat (7) dinon mein padh liya karo aur us se zyada ( qirat ( mat karna."
2733,"Auzai ne kaha : mujhey Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir ne ( umr ( bin-Hakam bin Soban se hadis sunai, kaha : mujhey abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey Abdullah ! falan shakhs ki tarah na ho jana wo raat ko qiyam karta tha, phir us ne raat ka qiyam tark kar diya."
2734,"Abdur-Razzaq ne kaha : hamein ibne-Juraij ne khabar di, kaha : maine Ata se suna wo kehtey they ke abu Abbas ne unko khabar di ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko itlaa mili ke main rozey rakhta hon, lagaataar rakhta hun aur raat bhar qiyam karta hun, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey paigham bheja ya meri Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mulaqat hui to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya mujhey nahi bataya gaya ke tum rozey rakhtey ho aur (koi roza ( nahi chhodtey aur raat bhar Namaz padhtey ho? tum aisa na karo kyonke ( tumharey waqt mein se) tumhari aankh ka bhi hissey hai. (ke wo neend ke doran mein aaraam karey) aur tumhari jaan ka bhi hissey hai. aur tumharey ghar walon ka bhi hissey hai. lihaza tum rozey rakho bhi aur tark bhi karo, Namaz padho aaraam bhi karo, aur har das din mein se aik din ka roza rakho aur tumhen ( baqi ( nau (9) dinon ka ( bhi) ajr milega. kaha : aey Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mein khud ko us se zyada taqat rakhney wala paata hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : to phir Dawud (Alaihissalam) ke se rozey rakho . kaha : aey Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! Dawud (Alaihissalam) ke rozey kis tarah they? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo aik din roza rakhtey they aik din iftaar kartey they aur jab ( dushman se) aamna-saamna hota to bhagtey nahi they. kaha : aey Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! mujhey iski zamaanat kon dega (ke meri zindagi ka har din rozey se shumaar hoga? ( Ata ne kaha : main nahi janta ke unhon-ne hamesha roza rakhney ka zikr kis tarah kya. to Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is ne roza nahi rakha jisne ( waqfey (kuchh dinon) ke baghair ( hamesha roza rakha , us ne roza nahi rakha jisne hamesha roza rakha. us ne roza nahi rakha jisne hamesha roza rakha."
2735,"Muhammad-bin-Bakr ne ham se hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein ibne-Juraij ne isi sanad se (pichhli hadis ki tarah ( hadis sunai aur kaha ke abu Abbas ne unko khabar di. Imam Muslim (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : abu Abbas Saaib bin Farukh ahal Makka se hain, qaabile-bharosa aur Udool hain."
2736,"Shoba ne hamein Habib se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu Abbas ( Saaib bin Farukh ( se suna, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : aey Abdullah-bin-Amr ! tum hamesha ( bila-waqfa rozana) rozey rakhtey ho aur raat bhar qiyam kartey ho aur jab tum aisa hi karogey to ( aisa karne waley ki) aankhen andar dhans jaeyngi aur (jaag-jaag kar) kamzor ho jaaeingi, (aur jahan tak ajr ka talluq hai to ( jisne hamesha roza rakha , us ne roza na rakha , mahiney mein se teen din ke rozey poorey mahiney ke rozey maaney jaaeingey. maine kaha : main is se zyada ( rozey rakhney ( ki taqat rakhta hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum Dawud (Alaihissalam) ke rozey ki tarah rozey rakho, wo aik din roza rakhtey they aur aik din tark kartey they aur) dushman se) muqabley ke waqt bhaagtey nahi they."
2737,"Misar se riwayat hai, kaha : hamein Habib bin abi Sabit ne isi sanad ke sath (pichhli hadis ki tarah ( hadis sunai aur kaha : aur) hamesha rozey rakhney waley ki) jaan kamzor ho jaeygi."
2738,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Amr se, unhon-ne abu-Abbaas se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se irshad farmaya : kya mujhey khabar nahi di gaee ke tum raat bhar qiyam kartey ho aur) rozana ( din ka roza rakhtey ho? maine kaha : main ye kaam karta hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum ye kaam karogey to ( iska nateeja ye hoga ke) tumhari aankhen andar ko dhans jaeyngi aur tumhari jaan kamzor ho jaeygi. tum par tumhari aankh ka haq hai. tumhari apni zaat ka haq hai. aur tumharey ghar walon ka haq hai. qiyam karo aur neend bhi lo, roza rakho bhi aur roza chhodo bhi."
2739,"hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Amr-bin-Dinar se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Amr bin Aus se aur unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Allah Taala ke nazdeek sabse pasandida ( nafli ( rozey Dawud (Alaihissalam) ke rozey hain aur Allah Taala ke nazdeek sabse pasandida ( nafli ( Namaz Dawud (Alaihissalam) ki Namaz hai. wo aadhi raat tak sotey they aur iska aik tehai qiyam kartey they aur uske ( aakhiri ( chhatey hissey mein so jatey they. aur aik din roza rakhtey they aur aik din iftaar kartey ( roza na rakhtey ( they."
2740,"hamein ibne-Juraij ne khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Amr-bin-Dinar ne khabar di ke unko Amr bin Aus ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se (ye ( khabar di ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah ke nazdeek sabse pasandida rozey Dawud (Alaihissalam) ke rozey hain. wo aadha zamana rozey rakhtey they. aur Allah Taala ke nazdeek sabse pasandida Namaz Dawud (Alaihissalam) ki Namaz hai, wo aadhi raat tak sotey they phir qiyam kartey they, phir iske aakhiri hissey mein so jatey they, wo aadhi raat ke baad ka aik tehai hissey qiyam kartey they. main (ibne-Juraij ( ne Amr-bin-Dinar se puchha : kya Amr bin Aus ye kehtey they : wo aadhi raat ke baad raat ka tehai hissey qiyam kartey they? unhon-ne jawab diya : haan."
2741,"Abu-Qilaba (bin Zaid-bin Aamir visual injury) no kaha: mujhey abu-Maleeh ne khabar di, kaha: main tumharey walid ke sath saiyedna Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaya to unhon-ne hamein hadis sunai to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke saamney merey rozon ka zikr kiya gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey yahan tashrif laaey, maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye chamdey ka ka ek takiya rakha jis mein khajoor ki chhaal bhari hui thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) zamin par baith gaey aur takiya merey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke beech mein a gaya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujhey farmaya: kya tumhen har mahiney mein se teen din (key rosey) kafi nahi? Maine kaha Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (is se zyada) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya: panch. Maine kaha Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (is se zyada) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) no farmaya: saat (7). Maine kaha Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (is se zyada) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) no farmaya: now (9). Maine kaha Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (is se zyada) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) no farmaya: gyara (11). Main kaha: aey Allah ke rasool! (Aur zyada.) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) no farmaya: Dawud (Alaihissalam) ke rozon se badh kar koi rozey nahi hain, aadha zamana, aik din roza rakhna aur aik din na rakhna."
2742,"Ziyad bin fayyaaz se riwayat hai, kaha : maine abu ayaaz se suna, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein farmaya : aik din ka roza rakho aur tumharey liye un ( dinon (ka ajr hai jo baqi hain. kaha : main is se zyada taqat rakhta hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : 2 din rozey rakho aur tumharey liye un ( dinon (ka ajr hai jo baqi hain. kaha : main is se zyada taqat rakhta hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : teen din rozey rakho aur tumharey liye un ( dinon (ka ajr hai jo baqi hain. kaha : main is se zyada taqat rakhta hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : char din rozey rakho aur tumharey liye un ( dinon (ka ajr hai jo baqi hain. kaha : main is se zyada taqat rakhta hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah ke nazdeek sabse zyada fazeelat waley rozey , yani Dawud (Alaihissalam) ke rozey ki tarah ( rozey ( rakho, wo aik din roza rakhtey they aur aik din chhod detey they."
2743,"Saeed bin Mina ne hamein hadis sunai, kaha : Abdullah-bin Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : aey Abdullah-bin-Amr ! mujhey khabar mili hai ke tum ( rozana ( din ka roza rakhtey ho aur raat bhar qiyam kartey ho, aisa mat karo kyonke tum par tumharey jism ka haq ( ada karna zaroori ( hai, tum par tumhari aankh ka haq ( ada karna zaroori hai) tum par tumhari biwi ka haq ( ada karna zaroori hai) rozey rakho aur tark bhi karo, har mahiney mein se teen din ke rozey rakh liya karo. ye sarey waqt ke rozon (ke barabar ( hain. maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! mere andar ( zyada rozey rakhney ki) quwwat hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum Dawud (Alaihissalam) ke rozey ki tarah ( rozey ( rakho, wo aik din roza rakhtey they aur aik din chhod detey they. wo kaha kartey they : kash! ! maine rukhsat ko qabool kya hota."
2744,"Sayeda Muaza al-Adwiya se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne Ummul-Momenin Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) se puchha ke kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) har maah mein teen rozey rakhtey they? unhon-ne kaha ke haan. phir puchha ke kin dinon main ( rozey rakhtey they? ( unhon-ne kaha ke kuchh parwah na kartey, kisi bhi din roza rakh letey they."
2745,Hazrat Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse poochha. ya kisi aur shakhs se puchha aur wo sun rahe they : . aey falan ! kya tum ne is mahiney ke beech mein rozey rakhey hain? us ne jawab diya nahi : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : to jab ( Ramazan mukammal karke ( rozey tark kar witr (har mahiney ( 2 din ke rozey rakhtey raho.
2746,"Hammad ne ghailan se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin Mabad zamani se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur puchha : aap kis tarah rozey rakhtey hain? uski baat se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghussey mein aa gaey, jab Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ghussa dekha to kehney lagey : ham Allah ke rab honey, Islam ke Deen honey aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke rasool honey par razi hain, ham Allah ke ghussey se aur us ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghussey se Allah ki panah mein aatey hain. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) baar-baar un kalimaat ko dohraney lagey yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ghussa thanda ho gaya, to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us shakhs ka kya hukm hai jo saal bhar (musalsal ( roza rakhta hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : na us ne roza rakha na us ne iftaar kya. ya farmaya, us ne roza nahi rakha us ne iftaar nahi kya. kaha : iska kya hukm hai jo 2 din roza rakhta hai aur aik din iftaar karta hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya koi uski taqat rakhta hai? puchha : iska kya hukm hai jo aik din roza rakhta hai aur aik din iftaar karta hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye Dawud (Alaihissalam) ka roza hai. puchha : iska kya hukm hai jo aik din roza rakhta hai aur 2 din iftaar karta hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mujhey pasand hai ke mujhey iski taqat mil jati. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : har mahiney ke teen rozey aur aik Ramazan (ke rozon ( se ( lekar doosrey ( Ramazan (ke rozey ( ye (amal ( sarey saal ke rozon (ke barabar ( hai. aur Arfa ke din ka roza main Allah se ummeed rakhta hun ke pichhley saal ke gunahon ka kaffara bin jaeyga aur agley saal ke gunahon ka bhi aur yaum aashoora ka roza , main Allah se ummeed rakhta hun ke pichhley saal ke gunahon ka kaffara bin jaeyga"
2747,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Ghelaan bin Jarir se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin Mabad zamani se suna, unhon-ne Hazrat abu Qatada Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aap ke rozon ke barey mein sawal kya gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) naraz ho gaey, is par Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ham Allah ke rab honey, Islam ke Deen honey, Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke rasool honey, aur bait ke taur par apni bait par razi hain. (jo ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ki.) kaha : iske baad aap se baghair waqfey (kuchh dinon) ke hamesha roza rakhney ( siyaamud-dehar) ke barey mein puchha gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is shakhs ne roza rakha na iftaar kya. iske baad aap se 2 din roza rakhney aur aik din tark karne ke barey mein puchha gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : uski taqat kon rakhta hai? kaha : aur aap se aik din roza rakhney aur 2 din tark karne ke barey mein puchha gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kash! ke Allah Taala ne hamein is kaam ki taqat di hoti . kaha : aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aik din roza rakhney aur aik din roza tark karne ke barey mein sawal kya gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye mere bhai Dawud (Alaihissalam) ka roza hai. kaha : aur aap se peer ka roza rakhney ke barey mein sawal kya gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye din hai jab main paida hua aur jis din mujhey ( rasool bana kar) bheja gaya. ya mujh par) Quran ( nazil kya gaya. kaha : iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : har maah ke teen rozey aur agley Ramazan tak Ramazan ke rozey hi hamesha ke rozey hain. kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yaume-Arfa ke rozey ke barey mein puchha gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye guzishta aur aainda saal ke gunahon ka kaffara bin jata hai. kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aashoora ke din ke rozey ke barey mein puchha gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo pichhley saal ke gunahon ka kaffara bin jata hai. Imam Muslim ne kaha : is hadis mein Shoba ki riwayat ( yun ( hai : unhon ( abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : aur aap se peer aur jumerat ke rozey ke barey mein sawal kya gaya. lekin ham ne jumerat ke zikr se sukoot kya hai, kyonke hamarey khayal mein ye ( rawi ka ( waham hai."
2748,"Muaaz-bin-Muaaz , Shababa aur Nazar-bin-Shumail sab ne Shoba se is sanad ke sath ( saabiq hadis ki tarah ( riwayat ki."
2749,"Aban Attar ne kaha : hamein Ghelaan bin Jarir ne isi sanad ke sath Shoba ki hadis ki manind (tarah) hadis bayan ki, magar unhon-ne (apni (us hadis mein peer ka zikr kiya , jumerat ka zikr nahi kya."
2750,"hamein Mehdi bin Memun ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne Ghelaan se baqi bachi pichhli sanad ke sath abu Qatada Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se peer ke rozey ke barey mein sawal kya gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main isi din paida hua aur isi din mujh par) Quran ( nazil kya gaya."
2751,Sabit ne Mutarrif se unhon-ne Hazrat Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un se. . padhi. ya kisi aur aadmi se. . padhi. farmaya : kya tum ne Shoban ke beech mein rozey rakhey hain? us ne jawab diya : nahi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum rozey khatm kar lo to 2 din ke rozey rakhna.
2752,abul-Ala ne Mutarrif se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik aadmi se puchha : kya tum ne is mahiney ke doran mein kuchh rozey rakhey hain? us ne jawab diya : nahi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum Ramazan ke rozey khatm kar lo to uski jagah 2 rozey rakh lena.
2753,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Mutarrif bin Shikhkhir ke bhatijey se hadis sunai, kaha : maine Mutarrif ko Hazrat Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kartey huey suna ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik aadmi se puchha : kya tum ne is mahiney yani Shoban ke beech (ya doran ( mein kuchh rozey rakhey hain? us ne jawab diya : nahi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey farmaya : jab tum Ramazan ke rozey khatm kar lo uske baad aik din ya 2 din ke rozey rakh lenaa. Shoba ne. padhi. jinko shak hua. padhi. kaha mera khayal hai ke aap ne 2 din ke rozey kaha tha."
2754,"nazar ne hamein khabar di, (kaha ( hamein Shoba ne khabar di, (kaha ( hamein Mutarrif ke bhatijey Abdullah-bin Hani ne isi sanad ke sath us (pichhli hadis) ki tarah hadis riwayat ki."
2755,abu Bishr ne Humaid bin Abdur-Rehman Himyari se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki. kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Ramazan ke baad sabse afzal rozey Allah ke mahiney Mohrim ke hain aur farz Namaz ke baad sabse afzal Namaz raat ki Namaz hai.
2756,"Jarir ne abdul-Malik-bin-Umair se unhon-ne Muhammad-bin Muntashir se unhon-ne Humaid bin Abdur-Rehman se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, wo usko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf se bayan kar rahe they. kaha : aap se malum kya gaya : farz Namaz ke baad kon si Namaz afzal hai aur maah Ramazan ke baad kon se rozey afzal hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : farz Namaz ke baad sabse afzal Namaz aadhi raat ki Namaz hai aur Ramazan ke mahiney ke baad sabse afzal rozey Allah ke mahiney Miharram ke rozey hain."
2757,Zayda ne abdul-Malik-bin-Umair se isi sanad ke sath Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se rozon ke zikr mein us (pichhli hadis) ki tarah riwayat ki.
2758,"hamein Ismael bin Jafar ne hadis sunai, (kaha : ( mujhey Sad bin Saeed Qais ne Umar-bin Sabit bin-Haaris khazraji se khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat abu Ayub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne unko hadis sunai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne Ramazan ke rozey rakhey . phir iske baad Shawaal ke chhey rozey rakhey to ye ( pura saal ( musalsal rozey rakhney ki tarah hai."
2759,Abdullah-bin-Numair ne baqi bachi pichhli sanad ke sath Hazrat abu Ayub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna. padhi. usi (pichhli hadis ki tarah .
2760,"Abdullah-bin-Mubarak ne Sad bin Saeed se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Umar-bin Sabit se suna, kaha : maine Hazrat Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya, padhi. usi (pichhli hadis) ki tarah ."
2761,"Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, ke aakhiri saat (7) raaton main Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ashaab mein se kuchh logon ko khuwab mein lailatul-qadr dikhaai gaee to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main dekhta hun ke tumhara khuwab aakhiri saat (7) raaton mein aik doosrey ke muwafiq ho gaya hai ab jo us ( lailatul-Qadr ( ko talash karna chahiye wo usey aakhiri saat (7) raaton mein talash kare. (Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke bayan ki hui mukammal alfaz aagey hadis : 2764 mein hain)"
2762,"Abdullah-bin-Dinar ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, farmaya : lailatul-Qadr ko) Ramazan ki) aakhiri saat (7) raaton mein talash karo."
2763,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Zohri se unhon-ne Salim se aur unhon-ne apne walid (Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, kaha : aik shakhs ne ( khuwab mein) dekha ke lailatul-Qadr sattaiswin raat hai. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main dekh raha hun ke tumhara khuwab aakhiri ashrey ke barey mein hai tum is ( lailatul-Qadr ( ko is ( ashrey ( ki taaq ( raaton ( mein talash karo."
2764,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, (kaha : ( mujhey Salim bin-Abdullah-bin umr ne khabar di ke unke walid ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se lailatul-Qadr ke barey mein suna, farma rahe they : tum mein se kuchh logon ko) khuwab mein) dikhaya gaya hai ke ye pehli saat (7) raaton mein hai aur tum mein se kuchh logon ko dikhaaya gaya hai ke ye baad mein aaney wali saat (7) raaton mein hai to tum usko baad mein aaney wali) aakhiri ( das raaton mein talash karo."
2765,"Aqba ne kaha : maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum is, yani lailatul-Qadr ko aakhiri das raaton mein talash karo, agar tum mein se koi kamzor pad jaey ya be-bas ho jaey to wo baqi ki saat (7) raaton main ( kisi sura susti kamzori se) maghloob na ho."
2766,"Shoba ne Jabla se riwayat ki kaha : maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hadis bayan kar rahe they ke aap ne farmaya : jo is raat ki talash mein ho to wo usey aakhiri das raaton mein talash kare."
2767,Shebani ne jabla aur Maharib se unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum lailatul-Qadr ke oqaat aakhiri das raaton mein talash karo. ya farmaya : aakhiri saat (7) raaton main ( talash karo. (
2768,"hamein abu-Taahir aur Hurmala bin Yahya ne hadis bayan ki, donon ne kaha : hamein ibne- Wahab ne khabar di (kaha : ( mujhey Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se khabar di, unhon-ne abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mujhey ( khuwab mein) shabe-qadr dikhai gaee phir mujhey mere ghar walon mein se kisi ne bedaar kar diya to wo mujhey bhulwa di gaee, tum usey baad mein aaney wali) aakhiri ( das raaton mein talash karo Hurmala ne (mujhey bhulwa di gaee ke bajaey) mein usey bhool gaya kaha,"
2769,"hamein Bakr ne ibne-Haad se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Muhammad-bin Ibrahim se, unhon-ne abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman se unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) un das dinon mein aetikaf kartey they jo mahiney ke darmyan mein hotey hain jab wo waqt aata ke bees raatein guzar jaatin aur ikkiswin raat ki aamad hoti to apne ghar lot jatey aur wo shakhs bhi lot jata jo aap ke sath aetikaf karta tha. phir aap aik mahiney, jis mein aap ne aetikaf kya tha us raat thahrey rahe jis mein aap ( ghar ( lot jaya kartey they. aap ne logon ko khutba diya, jo Allah Taala ne chaha iska hukm diya. phir farmaya : main un (beech key) das dinon ka aetikaf karta tha. phir mujh par ye baat khuli ke main us aakhiri ashrey ka aetikaf karun. to jis shakhs ne mere sath aetikaf kya hai wo apne aetikaf ki jagah hi mein raat Basar karey aur bila shubah maine ye raat khuwab mein dekhi hai iske baad wo mujhey bhula di gaee. lihaza tum usey aakhiri ashrey ki har taaq raat mein talash karo. maine apne aapko ( khuwab mein) dekha ke main pani aur mitti mein sajda kar raha hun. Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ikkiswin raat ham par barish hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz padhney ki jagah mein masjid (ki chhat ( tapak padi maine jab aap subah ki Namaz se farigh ho chukey they. aapko dekha to aap ke chehra Mubarak mitti aur pani se bheega hua tha."
2770,"Abdul-Azeez , yani Darawardi ne Yazeed (bin haad ( se unhon-ne Muhammad-bin Ibrahim se unhon-ne abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Ramazan mein darmyaaney ashrey ka aetikaf kartey they. ( aagey (us (pichhli hadis) ki tarah hadis bayan ki, albatta unhon-ne (apne aetikaf ki jagah mein raat guzarney ke bajaey) apne aetikaf ki jagah mein tika rahe, kaha aur kaha : aap ki peshani mitti aur pani se bhari hui thi."
2771,"ham se Umara-bin-Ghaziya Ansari ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Muhammad-bin Ibrahim se suna wo abu-Salma se hadis bayan kar rahe they, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik turki khemey ke andar jiske darwazey par chataai thi, Ramazan ke pahley ashrey mein aetikaf kya, phir darmyaney ashrey mein aetikaf kya. kaha : to aap ne chataai ko apne hath se pakad kar khemey ke aik koney mein kya, phir apna sar Mubarak khemey se bahar nikal kar logon se guftgu farmai, log aap ke qareeb ho gaey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine us shab ( qadr ( ko talash karne ke liye pahley ashrey ka aetikaf kya, phir maine darmyaaney ashrey ka aetikaf kya, phir mere paas ( Bukhari hadis : 813 mein hai : Jibreel ki) aamad hui to mujh se kaha gaya : wo aakhiri das raaton mein hai to ab tum mein se jo aetikaf karna chahey wo aetikaf kar ley , logon ne aap ke sath aetikaf kya. aap ne farmaya : aur mujhey wo aik taaq raat dikhai gaee aur ye ke main us (raat ( ki subah mitti aur pani mein sajda kar raha hun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ikkiswin raat ki subah ki, aur aap ne (is mein) subah tak qiyam kya tha phir barish hui to masjid (ki chhat ( tapak padi , maine mitti aur pani dekha iske baad jab aap subah ki Namaz se farigh ho kar bahar nikley to aap ki peshani aur naak ke kinarey donon mein mitti aur pani (ke nishanat ( maujood they aur ye aakhiri ashrey mein ikkiswin ki raat thi."
2772,"Hisham ne Yahya se aur unhon-ne abu-Salma se riwayat ki, kaha : ham ne aapas mein lailatul-Qadr ke barey mein baat cheet ki, phir main Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya wo mere dost they, maine kaha : kya aap hamarey sath nakhlistan mein nahi chalengey? wo nikley aur un (ke kandhon ( par dhari daar chadar thi, maine unse puchha : (kya (aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko lailatul-Qadr ka zikr kartey huey suna, tha? unhon-ne kaha : haan hamne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Ramazan ke beech waley ashrey mein aetikaf kya ham beeswin (raat ( ki subah ko (aetikaf se) nikley to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein khutba diya aur farmaya : mujhey lailatul-Qadr dikhai gaee aur ab main bhool gaya hun. mujhey bhula di gaee hai. isliye tum usko aakhiri ashrey ki har taaq raat mein talash karo aur maine dekha ke main (is raat) pani aur mitti mein sajda kar raha hun. to jisne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aetikaf kya hai wo wapas (aetikaf mein) chala jaey. kaha : ham wapas ho gaey aur hamein aasman mein badal ka koi tukda nazar nahi aa raha tha kaha : aik badli aai ham par barish hui yahan tak ke masjid ki chhat bah padi. wo khajoor ki shakhon se bani hui thi aur Namaz khadi ki gaee to maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha aap pani aur mitti mein sajda kar rahe they kaha : yahan tak ke maine aap ki peshani par mitti ka nishan bhi dekha."
2773,Mamar aur Auzai donon ne Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se isi sanad ke sath us (pichhli hadis) ke ham mana riwayat ki. aur un donon ki hadis mein hai : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz se ( farigh ho kar) paltey to maine aapko us haal mein dekha ke aap ki peshani aur naak ke kinarey par mitti ka nishan tha.
2774,"Muhammad-bin-Musanna aur Abu-Bakar bin khallad ne kaha : hamein Abdul-Aala ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Saeed ne abu-Nazara se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ramazan ke darmiyaney ashrey ka aetikaf kya us se pahley ke aap ke samney us usko khol diya jaey. aap lailatul-Qadr ko talash kar rahe they. jab ye (das raatein) khatm ho gain to aap ne hukm diya aur un khemon ko ukhada gaya phir (wo raat) aap par waazeh kar di gaee ke wo aakhiri ashrey mein hai. is par aap ne (khemey laganey ka ( hukm diya to unko dobara laga diya gaya. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) nikal kar logon ke samney aaey aur farmaya : aey logo ! mujh par lailatul-Qadr waazeh kar di gaee aur main tum ko iske barey mein batane ke liye nikla to 2 aadmi (eik doosrey par) apne haq ka dawa kartey huey aaey unke sath shaitan tha. is par wo mujhey bhula di gaee. tum usey Ramazan ke aakhiri ashrey mein talash karo. tum nawin, saatwin aur paanchwein (raat) mein talash karo. ( abu-Nazara ne) kaha : maine kaha : abu-Saeed ! hamari nisbat aap us ginti ko zyada jantey hain unhon-ne kaha : haan ham usey jaanney ke tum se zyada haqdaar hain. kaha maine puchha : nawin, saatwin, aur paanchwin se kya murad hai? unhon-ne jawab diya : jab ikkiswin raat guzarti hai to wahi raat jiske baad baaiswin aati hai wahi nawin hai aur jab teiswin raat guzarti hai to wahi jiske baad (aakhir se gintey huey saatwen raat aati hai) saatwin hai iske baad jab pachiswin raat guzarti hai to wahi jiske baad paanchwein raat aati hai) paanchwin hai. ibne- khallad ne, aik doosrey par haq ka dawa kartey huey, ki jagah, aapas mein jhagdaa kartey huey, kaha."
2775,Basar-bin-Saeed ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin Anees (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mujhey shabe-qadr dikhai gaee phir mujhey bhula di gaee. uski subah main apne aapko dekhta hun ke pani aur mitti mein sajda kar raha hun. kaha : teisween raat ham par barish hui. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein Namaz padhai phir aap ne ( rukh ( phera to aap ki peshani aur naak par pani aur mitti ke nishanat they. kaha : aur Abdullah-bin Anees (Raziallahu anhu) kaha kartey they ( lailatul-Qadr ( teeswin hai.
2776,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : lailatul-Qadr ko Ramazan ki aakhiri das raaton mein talash karo.
2777,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Abda aur Aasim bin abi Najood se riwayat ki, un donon ne Hazrat zirr-bin-Hubaish (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they. maine Hazrat Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se sawal kya, maine kaha : aap ke bhai Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain jo saal bhar (raat ko) qiyam karega. wo Lailatul-Qadr ko pa lega. unhon-ne farmaya : Allah un par raham farmaai unhon-ne chaha ke log (kam raaton ki ibadat par) qanaat na kar lein warna wo khub jantey hain ke wo Ramazan hi mein hai aur aakhiri ashrey mein hai aur ye bhi ke wo sattaiswin raat hai. phir unhon-ne istisnaa kiye ( insha-Allah kahey ( baghair qism kha kar kaha : wo sattaiswin raat hi hai is par maine kaha : abu munzir ! ye baat aap kis bina par kehtey hain? unhon-ne kaha is alamat ya nishani ki bina par jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein batai hai ke us din suraj nikalta hai uski shuaaein (numayan) nahi hotin."
2778,"Shoba ne kaha : maine Abda bin abi Lubaba se suna, wo Hazrat Zar bin Habish se hadis bayan kar rahe they. unhon-ne Hazrat Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki. kaha : Hazrat abi (Raziallahu anhu) ne lailatul-Qadr ke barey mein kaha : Allah ki qasam! main usko janta hun Shoba ne (riwaayat ke alfaz bayan kartey huey) kaha : mera ghalib guman hai ke ye wahi raat hai jis ( par poori raat (ke qiyam ka Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein hukm diya tha (aur ( wo sattaiswin raat hai. us fiqrey mein Shoba ne shak kya : ye wahi raat hai jiske barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein hukm diya aur kaha : iske barey mein mujhey mere aik sathi ne un ( Abda (ke hawale se hadis bayan ki."
2779,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney ham ne aapas mein lailatul-Qadr ka zikr kya to aap ne farmaya : tum mein se kis ko yad hai jab chaand nikla aur wo piyaa ley ke aik tukdey ki tarah tha ( wahi raat thi).
